%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rahul%20Gandhi%20Once%20Again%20Targets%20PM%20Modi%20Over%20Fresh%20Adani%20Allegations%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F31181250%2FScreenshot-2023-08-31-at-6.12.02-PM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Congress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20on%20Thursday%2C%20August%2031%2C%20once%20again%20targeted%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20for%20his%20alleged%20association%20with%20billionaire%20Gautam%20Adani%2C%20whose%20conglomerate%20has%20once%20again%20come%20under%20a%20cloud%20after%20a%20new%20investigation%20disclosed%20details%20of%20its%20offshore%20operations%20that%20could%20run%20foul%20of%20Indian%20regulations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGandhi%2C%20who%20is%20in%20Mumbai%20for%20the%20two-day%20meeting%20of%20the%20opposition%20INDIA%20bloc%2C%20addressed%20the%20media%20and%20accused%20the%20Modi%20government%20of%20protecting%20Adani%20and%20his%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReading%20out%20headlines%20of%20two%20global%20newspapers%20that%20published%20the%20new%20allegations%2C%20Gandhi%20asked%20why%20the%20Union%20government%20and%20Modi%20are%20%E2%80%9Cshying%20away%E2%80%9D%20from%20probing%20these%20%E2%80%9Cserious%20allegations%E2%80%9D%20against%20Adani%20and%20his%20brother%20Vinod%20Adani.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20allegations%20%E2%80%93%20published%20by%20UK%20newspapers%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Guardian%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3EFinancial%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20%E2%80%93%20are%20based%20on%20documents%20obtained%20by%20the%20Organised%20Crime%20and%20Corruption%20Reporting%20Project%20(OCCRP).%20The%20thrust%20of%20the%20reports%20is%20that%20Adani%20family%20partners%20used%20%E2%80%9Copaque%20funds%20via%20Mauritius%E2%80%9D%20to%20invest%20in%20its%20own%20group%20stocks%2C%20in%20violation%20of%20Indian%20regulations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Fadani-group-stocks-offshore-investments-reports%5C%22%3EDocuments%20Suggest%20Adani%20Family%20Associates%20May%20Have%20Bought%20Shares%20to%20Fuel%20Group%E2%80%99s%20Growth%3A%20Reports%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Adani%20Group%20has%20rubbished%20the%20%E2%80%9Crecycled%E2%80%9D%20allegations%20as%20an%20attempt%20to%20revive%20%E2%80%9Cmeritless%E2%80%9D%20accusations%20made%20by%20the%20US-based%20short%20seller%20Hindenburg%20Research%2C%20which%20accused%20it%20of%20%E2%80%9Cbrazen%20stock%20manipulation%20and%20accounting%20fraud%E2%80%9D%20in%20January%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20recent%20investigations%20by%20the%20newspapers%20have%20identified%20two%20persons%2C%20Nasser%20Ali%20Shaban%20Ahli%20from%20the%20United%20Arab%20Emirates%20and%20Chang%20Chung-Ling%20from%20Taiwan%20%E2%80%A6%20They%20are%20both%20foreign%20nationals.%20Why%20are%20they%20allowed%20to%20play%20a%20role%20in%20this%3F%20Adani%E2%80%99s%20company%20handles%20infrastructure%2C%20airports%2C%20ports%20in%20India.%20What%20are%20these%20two%20foreign%20nationals%2C%20especially%20a%20Chinese%20man%2C%20doing%20here%3F%E2%80%9D%20Gandhi%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGandhi%20added%20that%20when%20foreign%20leaders%20travel%20to%20India%20to%20participate%20in%20the%20G20%20summit%2C%20the%20most%20pertinent%20question%20each%20of%20them%20could%20ask%20is%20about%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20reasons%20for%20%E2%80%9Cshielding%E2%80%9D%20Adani.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20ought%20to%20ask%20why%20is%20our%20prime%20minister%20protecting%20Adani.%20What%20is%20this%20special%20company%20and%20why%20is%20it%20getting%20a%20free-ride%20in%20India%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20SEBI%20%5Bmarket%20regulator%5D%20official%20who%20was%20in%20charge%20of%20investigating%20Adani%E2%80%99s%20company%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fbusiness%2Fndtv-appoints-ex-sebi-chief-uk-sinha-welspun-ceo-as-independent-director%2Farticle66669257.ece%23%3A~%3Atext%3DAdani%2520group%252Downed%2520NDTV%2520Ltd%2CDipali%2520Goenka%2520as%2520Independent%2520Directors.%5C%22%3Etoday%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20director%20of%20NDTV%2C%20a%20media%20channel%20that%20Adani%20owns.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20reference%20by%20Gandhi%20was%20about%20Upendra%20Kumar%20Sinha%2C%20who%20was%20head%20of%20SEBI%20in%202014%2C%20when%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fworld%2F2023%2Faug%2F31%2Fmodi-linked-adani-family-secretly-invested-in-own-shares-documents-suggest-india%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Guardian%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20he%20was%20alerted%20about%20%E2%80%9Cindications%20that%20%5BAdani-linked%5D%20money%20may%20have%20found%20its%20way%20to%20stock%20markets%20in%20India%20as%20investment%20and%20disinvestment%20in%20the%20Adani%20Group%E2%80%9D.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20SEBI%20was%C2%A0%E2%80%9Cunderstood%20to%20be%20investigating%20into%20the%20dealings%20of%20the%20Adani%20Group%20of%20companies%20in%20the%20stock%20market%E2%80%9D%20but%20after%20Modi%20was%C2%A0elected%20in%20May%202014%2C%20SEBI%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Capparent%20interest%20seemed%20to%20disappear%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESinha%20was%20in%20March%20this%20year%20appointed%20as%20an%20independent%20director%20of%20NDTV%2C%20which%20the%20Adani%20Group%20acquired%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGandhi%20continued%2C%20%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20no%20level%20playing%20field%20in%20India.%20Adani%20can%20just%20about%20buy%20anything%20that%20he%20wishes.%20Be%20it%20the%20Dharavi%20project%20or%20any%20airport%2C%20Adani%20can%20simply%20take%20over%20anything%20in%20the%20country.%20One%20man%20is%20able%20to%20buy%20whatever%20asset%20he%20wishes.%20He%20is%20accused%20of%20wrongdoings.%20One%20billion%20dollars%20have%20definitely%20been%20moved%20out%20of%20India%20and%20brought%20back%20to%20India%20from%20suspicious%20channels%20and%20the%20PM%20is%20duty-bound%20to%20find%20where%20the%20money%20is.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEach%20time%20I%20speak%20about%20Adani%2C%20Modi%20gets%20restless.%20The%20last%20time%20I%20spoke%2C%20my%20parliament%20membership%20was%20revoked.%20When%20the%20party%20panics%2C%20it%20resorts%20to%20such%20extreme%20steps%2C%E2%80%9D%20Gandhi%20said%2C%20speaking%20about%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmodi-government-calls-five-day-special-session-of-parliament-from-september-18%5C%22%3Especial%20session%20of%20parliament%3C%2Fa%3E%20called%20by%20the%20government%20on%20Thursday%20from%20September%2018.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20Hindenburg%20report%20was%20released%2C%20the%20opposition%20demanded%20a%20joint%20parliamentary%20probe%20into%20the%20allegations.%20While%20the%20government%20did%20not%20discuss%20the%20demand%2C%20Gandhi%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Frahul-gandhis-conviction-in-surat-case-pushes-limits-of-defamation-law%5C%22%3Econvicted%20in%20a%20defamation%20case%3C%2Fa%3E%20soon%20after%20he%20raised%20the%20issue%20in%20parliament%2C%20leading%20to%20his%20disqualification%20as%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20am%20raising%20this%20issue%20simply%20because%20this%20is%20about%20the%20reputation%20of%20our%20country.%20We%20are%20only%20asking%20the%20PM%20to%20announce%20an%20investigation%20into%20the%20allegations%20levelled%20against%20the%20Adani%20Group%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20Congress%20leader%2C%20who%20spoke%20for%2020%20minutes%20and%20took%20three%20questions%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20National%20Developmental%20Inclusive%20Alliance%20(INDIA)%20parties%20are%20set%20for%20their%20third%20meeting%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20where%20they%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fat-indias-mumbai-meet-seat-sharing-to-take-back-seat-as-focus-is-on-common-programme-vision%5C%22%3Eexpected%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20forge%20consensus%20on%20the%20common%20m