I%20interrupted%20you%2C%20please%20come%20to%20the%20second.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20aspect%20in%20terms%20of%20which%20%5Blaw%20and%20order%20can%20be%20tackled%5D%20is%20the%20issue%20of%20filing%20these%20cases%20which%20are%20now%2C%20of%20course%2C%20some%20cases%20with%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20etc%2C%20those%20cases%20which%20will%20go%20to%20Assam%2C%20cases%20which%20are%20within%20%5BManipur%5D%20itself.%20Opening%20up%20of..%20You%20have%20to%20open%20up%20supply%20lines%2C%20because%20if%20you%20block%20supply%20lines%2C%20whether%20it%E2%80%99s%20by%20the%20Meiteis%20or%20by%20the%20Kukis%20etc%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20good%20and%20so%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EForcibly%2C%20those%20highways%20must%20be%20cleared%20of%20blockade.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20highways%20must%20be%20cleared%20of%20blockades.%20You%20can%20have%2C%20I%20think%20initially%2C%20you%20still%20need%2C%20possibly%20for%20the%20next%20six%20months%2C%20you%20still%20need%20the%20buffer%20zones%2C%20as%20still%20the%20situation%20and%20the%20violence%20comes%20down.%20A%20couple%20of%20steps%20they%20have%20taken%2C%20which%20I%20have%20seen%2C%20which%20I%E2%80%99ve%20mentioned%20partly%20also%20earlier.%20Like%2C%20they%20posted%20some%20tribal%20officers%20to%20the%20hill%20districts%20who%20have%20now%20%E2%80%93%20All%20India%20Service%20officers%20%E2%80%93%20which%20gives%20some%20confidence%20to%20the%20people%20that%2C%20okay%20we%E2%80%99ve%20got%20people%20who%20we%20know%2C%20we%20can%20trust%20them%2C%20they%20have%20come%20to%20do%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYou%20also%20need%20to%20start%20what%20I%20call%E2%80%A6%20of%20course%2C%20the%20CBI%20has%20taken%20over%20some%20cases.%20But%20there%20are%20other%20cases%20where%20people%2C%20like%20yesterday%20you%20saw%2C%20three%20houses%20burned%20down.%20Which%20is%20what%20you%20are%20trying%20to%20basically%20send%20a%20message%20to%20the%20Kukis%20and%20the%20Zomi%20that%20you%20are%20not%20welcome%20back%20%5Bin%20Imphal%5D.%20Three%20months%20have%20gone%20by%2C%20we%E2%80%99ve%20half%20burnt%20your%20house%2C%20now%20we%20are%20completely%20burning%20down%20your%20houses.%20It%20sends%20a%20message%20that%20you%20don%E2%80%99t%20even%20think%20of%20coming%20back.%20Though%2C%20personally%2C%20I%20think%20none%20of%20them%20will%20come%20back%2C%20that%E2%80%99s%20another%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20again%20two-three%20weapons%20looted%20from%20residents%20of%20some%20director%20of%20health%20or%20something.%20I%20mean%2C%20you%20can%E2%80%99t%20allow%20this%20sort%20of%20slackness.%20Somebody%20has%20to%20be%20held%20responsible%2C%20which%20is%20why%20I%20said%2C%20dismiss%20the%20officers%20and%20they%20are%20both%20in%20the%20hill%20districts%20and%20in%20the%20valley.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENone%20of%20them%20have%20been%20dismissed%20so%20far.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20one.%20So%20the%20moment%20you%20dismiss%20them%2C%20you%20are%20sending%20a%20signal%20that%20this%20will%20not%20be%20tolerated.%20At%20least%20the%20next%20time%20somebody%20comes%20to%20loot%20the%20armoury%2C%20people%20will%20open%20fire.%20I%20mean%2C%20you%20just%20can%E2%80%99t%20allow%20that%20to%20happen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EYou%20know%2C%20as%20I%20hear%20you%20speak%2C%20the%20things%20you%20are%20suggesting%20they%20are%20obvious.%20They%20are%20things%20that%20should%20have%20been%20done%20immediately%20and%20yet%20they%20haven%E2%80%99t%20been%20done.%20What%20does%20that%20tell%20us%20about%20the%20attitude%20and%20performance%20of%20a%20whole%20lot%20of%20functioning%2C%20is%20not%20just%20the%20chief%20minister%2C%20but%20I%E2%80%99m%20not%20excluding%20it%2C%20but%20the%20DGP%2C%20the%20security%20advisor%2C%20the%20SPs%2C%20the%20whole%20administration%20of%20state%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETotally%20unprofessional.%20I%20you%20want%20to%20put%20it%2C%20I%20would%20even%20say%20incompetent.%20Because%20if%204%2C000%20weapons%20have%20been%20looted%20and%20by%20now%20you%20haven%E2%80%99t%20been%20doing%20raids.%20I%20mean%20you%20saw%2C%20cases%20when%20riots%20take%20place%20and%20so%20on%20and%20so%20forth%2C%20the%20first%20thing%20that%20you%20do%20if%20there%20are%20weapons%20have%20been%20used%20by%20anybody%2C%20people%20raid.%20The%20civilians%20have%20to%20feel%20a%20little%20bit%20uncomfortable%2C%20that%20this%20will%20not%20be%20%5Btolerated%5D.%20Therefore%2C%20the%20next%20time%20they%20try%20to%20do%20this%2C%20there%20will%20be%20second%20thoughts.%20Whereas%2C%20if%20they%20feel%20that%20nothing%20is%20going%20to%20happen%20to%20them%E2%80%A6%20%3Cstrong%3E(shrugs)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIn%20fact%2C%20by%20failing%20to%20raid%20you%E2%80%99re%20giving%20them%20%3Cem%3Ecarte%20blanche%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20you%E2%80%99re%20encouraging%20them%20to%20carry%20on.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYeah%2C%20you%E2%80%99re%20telling%20them%20that%20the%20government%20has%20actually%20told%20you%2C%20%E2%80%9CKeep%20the%20arms.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAre%20there%20other%20steps%20that%20you%20would%20advise%20to%20the%20home%20minister%2C%20if%20he%20hears%20you%2C%20to%20tackle%20law%20and%20order%3F%20One%20of%20them%20is%20to%20get%20back%20the%20weapons%2C%20raid%20if%20need%20be.%20The%20second%20is%20to%20file%20the%20case%20and%20prosecute%20them.%20Are%20there%20other%20steps%20in%20terms%20of%20law%20and%20order%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESee%2C%20these%20are%20the%20first%20steps.%20Then%2C%20you%20start%20the%20second%20process%20of%20what%20I%20call%20giving%20relief%2C%20rehabilitation%20and%20compensation%20part%20of%20it%E2%80%A6%20which%20is%20not%E2%80%A6%20but%20it%20is%20equally%20important%20because%20from%20the%20relief%20camps%20itself%20stories%20%5Bare%20emerging%20from%5D%20both%20sides%2C%20youngsters%20and%20all%2C%20are%20going%20now%20into%20what%20you%20call%20as%20you%20know%20%E2%80%9Cvillage%20defence%20forces%E2%80%9D%20and%20so%20on%20and%20so%20forth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20if%20you%20don%E2%80%99t%20give%20confidence%20to%20the%20youngsters%20that%20you%20are%20to%20go%20and%20study%20in%20the%20school%20or%20you%20are%20providing%20some%20online%20education%20and%20so%20on%2C%20within%20the%20relief%20camps%20itself%E2%80%A6%20but%20then%2C%20your%20first%20priority%20is%20to%20go%20and%20get%20arms%20training%20from%20civilians%20to%20protect%20your%20own%20villages%20%E2%80%93%20that%E2%80%99s%20a%20failure%20of%20the%20state.%20Because%20the%20state%20is%20supposed%20to%20protect%20the%20citizens.%20Uou%20don%E2%80%99t%20expect%20the%20citizens%20to%20take%20arms%20to%20protect%20themselves.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPeople%20like%20Harsh%20Mander%20who%20visited%20with%20his%20Karwan-e-Mohabbat%2C%20people%20from%20the%20Church%20who%20are%20present%20%E2%80%93%20including%20Meitei%20people%20in%20the%20valley%20%E2%80%93%20all%20tell%20me%20that%20the%20majority%20of%20the%20relief%20is%20being%20provided%20in%20the%20camps%2C%20not%20by%20the%20state%2C%20but%20by%20civil%20society%20groups%2C%20by%20the%20church%20and%20by%20Meitei%20organisations.%20In%20other%20words%2C%20the%20state%20has%20opted%20out%20of%20doing%20what%20it%20should%20be%20doing.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYes%2C%20I%20think%20that%20has%20been%2C%20one%2C%20absence.%20There%20are%20two-three%20things%20the%20state%20can%20do.%20The%20state%20has%20a%20limited%20capacity%2C%20I%20mean%20Manipur%20government%20is%20not%20like%2C%20you%20know%2C%20you%20would%20find%2C%20say%20Maharashtra%20or%20Karnataka%20or%20a%20Delhi%20government.%20etc.%2C%20where%20%E2%80%93%20you%20know%2C%20the%20capacity%20of%20the%20state%20is%20limited.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20small%20state%2C%20a%20small%20number%20of%20offices.%20Very%20large%20community%20organisations%20are%20there%2C%20so%20it%E2%80%99s%20all%20right%20that%20the%20community%20organisations%20come%20forward.%20But%20the%20state%20must%20provide%20money%2C%20provide%20%5Bprefab%5D%20housing%2C%20they%20must%20be%20able%20to%20provide%20doctors%20from%20government%20hospitals%20because%20most%20of%20the%20hospitals%20are%20medical%20colleges%20and%20so%20on.%20They%20should%20be%20able%20to%20provide%20clothing%20and%20so%20on%20and%20so%20forth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20relief%20and%20compensation%20which%20would%20have%20been%20expected%20from%20a%20state%20has%20not%20come.%20It%E2%80%99s%20actually%20a%20tribute%20to%20the%20strength%20of%20community%20organisations%20in%20Manipur%20%E2%80%93%20both%20Meitei%20as%20well%20as%20the%20Christian%20organisations%20%E2%80%93%20that%20they%20have%20been%20able%20to%20get%E2%80%A6%20In%20fact%2C%20we%20have%20an%20IAS%20officer%20in%20Manipur%E2%80%93%20current%2C%20Meitei%20officer%20%E2%80%93%20who%20has%20actually%20reached%20out%20to%20the%20IAS%20community%20through%20his%20batchmates%2C%20and%20money%20has%20actually%20flowed%20from%20our%20WhatsApp%20groups%20to%20his%20NGO%2C%20which%20is%20actually%E2%80%A6.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBut%20that%20is%20an%20individual%20taking%20an%20initiative%2C%20not%20the%20state.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERather%20than%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIn%20fact%2C%20you%20mentioned%20the%20need%20for%20doctors%20and%20medical%20care%2C%20you%20mentioned%20the%20need%20for%20money.%20Newspaper%20reports%2C%20and%20I%E2%80%99m%20going%20entirely%20by%20them%2C%20suggest%20that%20very%20little%20of%20the%20money%20that%20was%20promised%20has%20actually%20reached%20people%2C%20whether%20it%E2%80%99s%20up%20in%20the%20hills%2C%20whether%20it%E2%80%99s%20down%20in%20the%20valley.%20And%20as%20far%20as%20the%20Kukis%20are%20concerned%20in%20the%20hills%2C%20there%20is%20a%20real%20crisis%20of%20medical%20treatment.%20Doctors%20are%20absent%2C%20medicine%20supplies%20are%20absent%2C%20they%E2%80%99re%20having%20to%20travel%20in%20some%20instances%20to%20Nagaland%20or%20Assam.%20And%20some%20reports%20suggest%20that%20people%20who%20are%20critically%20ill%20have%20died.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYes%2C%20I%20think%20my%20information%20itself%20tells%20me%20that%20the%20number%20of%20people%20who%20have%20died%20in%20these%20camps%20has%20crossed%2050.%20So%20when%20you%20say%20that%20100%20and%20some%20odd%20people%20were%20killed%20in%20the%20riots%2C%20you%20almost%20got%20another%2035-40%25%20of%20people%20who%20have%20died%20post%20riots%2C%20in%20the%20camps%20out%20of%20various%20illnesses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThis%20is%20because%20of%20the%20inefficiency%20or%20incompetence%20of%20the%20state%20administration.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYes%2C%20it%20not%20being%20able%20to%20provide%20adequate%20health%E2%80%A6%20In%20fact%2C%20I%20would%20have%20expected%20even%20from%20the%20government%20of%20India%20that%20they%20should%20have%20started%20health%20facilities%20from%20AIIMS%20and%20so%20on%20and%20so%20forth%2C%20doctors%20from%20various%20places%20should%20have%20been%20sent.%2030%2C%2040%20doctors%20should%20have%20been%20sent%2C%20by%20rotation%2C%20for%20a%20month%20or%20two%20months%20to%20many%20of%20these%20relief%20camps%20just%20to%20provide%20basic%20health%20facilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F31154026%2F1c13ccf9-051a-4b3c-80ea-a49bbff34074_2067x1151.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F31154026%2F1c13ccf9-051a-4b3c-80ea-a49bbff34074_2067x1151.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F31154026%2F1c13ccf9-051a-4b3c-80ea-a49bbff34074_2067x1151-300x167.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F31154026%2F1c13ccf9-051a-4b3c-80ea-a49bbff34074_2067x1151-1024x570.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-670858%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22668%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20relief%20camp%20in%20Moirang%2C%20Manipur.%20Photo%3A%20Imaad%20ul%20Hasan%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENot%20only%20have%20they%20not%20been%20sent%20by%20the%20Government%20of%20India%2C%20but%20it%20seems%20that%20it%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20even%20occurred%20to%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20that%20this%20is%20needed.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%2C%20they%20are%20aware.%20I%20think%20the%20Union%20home%20minister%20had%20promised%20that%2050%20medical%20teams%20would%20be%20sent.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAbsolutely%2C%20when%20he%20was%20there%20but%20they%20have%20not%20gone.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20haven%E2%80%99t%20gone.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHe%20made%20a%20promise%20and%20even%20three%20months%20later%2C%20the%20government%20has%20failed%20to%20fulfil%20it.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20that%20is%20why%20the%20condition%20in%20the%20camps%20are%20so%20poor%2C%20and%20many%20of%20them%20are%E2%80%A6%20now%2C%20of%20course%2C%20slowly%20the%20prefabricated%20houses%20%5Bare%20coming%20up%5D%20because%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20panel%20has%2C%20you%20know%2C%20pointed%20out%20the%20total%20inadequacy%20of%20what%20has%20been%20provided.%20I%20expect%20things%20to%20improve%20now%20but%20this%20is%20something%20which%20should%20have%20been%20done%20in%20the%20first%2015-30%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWe%E2%80%99re%20coming%20to%20the%20end%20of%20what%20I%20call%20the%20first%20section%2C%20which%20is%20restoring%20law%20and%20order%2C%20relief%20and%20rehabilitation.%20You%E2%80%99ve%20painted%20a%20picture%20which%20is%20deeply%20depressing.%20The%20essential%20steps%20to%20resolve%20order%20are%20obvious%20but%20they%E2%80%99re%20not%20being%20taken.%20Who%20knows%20when%20they%20will%20be%20taken%3F%20The%20steps%20for%20relief%20and%20rehabilitation%20are%20obvious%2C%20they%20are%20not%20being%20taken%20%E2%80%93%20with%20the%20exception%20of%20housing.%20Nothing%20else%20is%20really%20happening.%20So%20when%20will%20we%20have%20a%20restoration%20of%20law%20and%20order%3F%20When%20will%20people%20be%20given%20relief%20and%20rehabilitation%3F%20It%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20look%20as%20if%20there%E2%80%99s%20an%20endpoint%20in%20sight.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYeah%2C%20I%20expect%20that%E2%80%A6%20See%2C%20it%20is%20unfortunate%20because%20again%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20failure%20of%20the%20government%20that%20I%20expect%20that%E2%80%A6%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20panel%20has%20now%20given%20its%20report.%20They%20have%20pointed%20out%20the%20inadequacies%20etc.%2C%20that%20have%20now%20been%20communicated%20to%20the%20state%20government%20and%20I%20think%20next%20week%20the%20response%20of%20the%20state%20government%20and%20the%20central%20government%20will%20come%20as%20to%20what%20they%20have%20done.%20I%20expect%20that%20again%20the%20state%20government%20and%20central%20government%20will%2C%20to%20avoid%20being%20criticised%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20say%20that%20we%20are%20rushing%20some%20equipment%2C%20some%20doctors%20and%20so%20on%20and%20so%20forth%20to%20show%20that%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThat%E2%80%99s%20just%20face-saving.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%E2%80%99s%20face-saving%2C%20because%20it%20should%20have%20been%20done%20much%20before%20this%20because%E2%80%A6%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESo%20we%20failed%20as%20a%20state%20in%20restoring%20law%20and%20order%20and%20relief%20and%20rehabilitation.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYes%2C%20we%20have.%20We%E2%80%99ve%20had%20riots%2C%20you%20know%2C%20100%20people%20%5Bdying%5D%20is%20not%20something%20which%20is%20people%20in%20India%2C%20the%20size%20of%20India%2C%20we%20have%20not%20faced%20before.%20But%20in%20all%20cases%20which%20have%20happened%20%E2%80%93%20whether%20it%E2%80%99s%20in%20UP%2C%20whether%20it%E2%80%99s%20in%20Bihar%2C%20whether%20it%E2%80%99s%20in%20Kerala%2C%20whether%20it%E2%80%99s%20%5Banywhere%20else%5D%20%E2%80%93%20the%20State%20has%20responded%20very%20quickly.%20In%20any%20riot%20situation%2C%20the%20state%20responds%20very%20quickly%20and%20if%20you%20don%E2%80%99t%20respond%20quickly%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20real%20failure.%20That%E2%80%99s%20where%20the%20administration%20%E2%80%93%20officers%20also%20%E2%80%93%20are%20responsible.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThis%20is%20where%20Manipur%20is%20a%20clear%20outlier.%20We%20haven%E2%80%99t%20responded%20quickly.%20In%20fact%2C%20we%20know%20what%20we%20should%20be%20doing%2C%20and%20we%E2%80%99re%20not%20doing%20it.%20It%E2%80%99s%20very%20hard%20to%20move%20further%2C%20but%20academically%2C%20I%20will.%20I%20imagine%2C%20side%20by%20side%20with%20tackling%20law%20and%20order%20%E2%80%93%20which%20as%20you%20pointed%20out%2C%20is%20being%20done%20ineffectively%2C%20if%20it%E2%80%99s%20being%20done%20at%20all%20%E2%80%93%20the%20government%20also%20needs%20to%20turn%20its%20attention%20to%20the%20very%20difficult%2C%20intractable%2C%20political%20issues.%20Are%20the%20talks%20that%20are%20happening%20with%20the%20COCOMI%2C%20on%20the%20one%20hand%20from%20the%20Meiti%20side%2C%20and%20with%20the%20ITLF%20from%20the%20Kuki%20side%2C%20the%20right%20way%20of%20tackling%20this%20political%20issue%3F%20Or%20should%20the%20government%20be%20reaching%20out%20through%20civil%20society%20groups%20and%2C%20perhaps%20through%20highly%20regarded%20individuals%20who%20both%20sides%20respect%20like%20for%20example%2C%20Ratan%20Thiyam%3F%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESee%2C%20the%20government%20has%20started%2C%20I%20think%20to%20an%20extent%20that%20fact%2C%20that%20the%20dialogues%20have%20started%20even%20though%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20still%20with%20one%20party%2C%20one%20party%20rather%20than%20everybody%20sitting%20across%20the%20table.%20That%20stage%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20yet%20come%20because%20of%20the%20acute%20mistrust%20between%20the%20communities.%20The%20process%20has%20started.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20think%20the%20steps%20on%20law%20and%20order%2C%20which%20I%20mentioned%20earlier%3B%20the%20steps%20on%20relief%2C%20rehabilitation%20and%20compensation.%20The%20compensation%2C%20so%20far%2C%20has%20been%20very%20inadequate.%20People%20have%20lost%2C%20I%20mean%20some%20in%20some%20places%2C%20crores%20of%20rupees%2C%20and%20you%20are%20then%20saying%20I%E2%80%99ll%20give%20you%20Rs%203%20lakh%2C%20Rs%205%20lakh%20%E2%80%93%20which%20are%20still%20not%20been%20given.%20So%2C%20this%20whole%20issue%20of%20assessing%20what%20has%20been%20the%20damage%20done%2C%20finding%20out%20who%20the%20people%2C%20etc%2C.%20This%20is%20something%20which%20should%20have%20been%20done%2C%20still%20not%20done.%20But%20let%20us%20assume%20that%20those%20are%20done.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20are%20all%20steps%2C%20as%20part%20of%20what%20I%20call%20as%20the%20background%20to%20the%20political%20process%2C%20which%20is%20in%20one%20sense%2C%20at%20the%20moment%20they%E2%80%99re%20talking%20of%20separate%20administration.%20I%20still%20put%20it%20as%20%E2%80%93%20if%20you%20are%20looking%20at%20the%20territory%20integrity%20of%20Manipur%20being%20preserved%2C%20you%20are%20looking%20at%20as%20greater%20autonomy%2C%20whether%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20Sixth%20Schedule%20status%2C%20whether%20it%E2%80%99s%20something%20more.%20These%20are%20still%2C%20I%20put%20it%20as%2C%20one-two%20years%20down%20the%20line.%20Because%20the%20Manipur%20issue%20of%20autonomy%20to%20the%20hills%2C%20is%20also%20linked%20to%20t