ow%20you%20could%20have%20reacted%20to%20those%20signs%20is%20different%2C%20but%20they%20were%20definitely%20there%20and%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20see%20any%20sort%20of%20precautionary%20steps%20taken%20%E2%80%93%20either%20as%20a%20state%20or%20the%20central%20level%20%E2%80%93%20to%20handle%20those%20warning%20signs.%20If%20%5Bany%20steps%5D%20were%20%5Btaken%5D%2C%20they%20have%20not%20been%20disclosed%20publicly.%20But%20the%20warning%20signs%20are%20there.%20I%E2%80%99ve%20talked%20to%20people%20in%20the%20administration%20in%20Manipur%2C%20I%E2%80%99ve%20talked%20to%20people%20in%20the%20armed%20forces%20and%20so%20on.%20Everybody%20says%20the%20warning%20signs%20were%20there.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEveryone%20saw%20that%2C%20everyone%20knew%20there%20were%20warning%20signs.%20No%20one%20acted.%20You%20can%20only%20blame%20yourself.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELet%E2%80%99s%20come%20to%20the%20background%20issues.%20Let%E2%80%99s%20go%20through%20them%20one%20by%20one.%20First%20I%E2%80%99ll%20take%20up%20the%20issues%20raised%20by%20the%20Meitei%2C%20then%20I%E2%80%99ll%20come%20to%20the%20issues%20raised%20by%20the%20Kuki%2C%20just%20for%20simplicity.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Meitei%20believe%20that%20the%20Kuki%20are%20involved%20in%20poppy%20cultivation%20and%20in%20illegal%20drug%20trade.%20What%20we%20know%20from%20the%20interview%20that%20Thounaojam%20Brinda%20has%20given%20me%20and%20she%E2%80%99s%20given%20it%20also%20to%20other%20%5Boutlets%5D.%20In%20fact%2C%20she%20alleges%2C%20that%20the%20chief%20minister%20has%20been%20protecting%20a%20drug%20lord%20who%20is%20a%20BJP%20functionary%20and%20his%20wife%20too%2C%20she%20alleges%2C%20is%20involved.%20So%20is%20this%20charge%20made%20by%20the%20Meitei%20against%20the%20Kuki%2C%20pointing%20fingers%20only%20in%20one%20direction%3F%20Or%20are%20they%20all%20involved%20in%20it%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20think%20everybody%20is%20involved.%20There%E2%80%99s%20no%2C%20I%20mean%20it%E2%80%99s%20been%20there%20in%20the%20past%20%E2%80%93%20the%20drugs%2C%20both%20within%20Manipur%20as%20well%20as%20outside.%20Manipur%20has%20a%20history%20of%20drug%20problems%2C%20starting%20from%20HIV%2C%20then%20the%20whole%20community%20got%20together%20to%2C%20you%20know%2C%20sort%20of%20tackle%20that.%20So%20it%E2%80%99s%20something%20which%20is%20there.%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20think%20its%E2%80%A6%20Everybody%20is%20involved%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20fact.%20And%20how%20they%E2%80%99re%20going%20to%20tackle%20it%20is%E2%80%A6%20I%20think%20it%E2%80%99s%20the%20Narcotics%20Control%20Bureau%2C%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%E2%80%A6%20all%20these%20people%20are%20now%20to%20see%2C%20you%20know%2C%20the%20PMLA%20and%20so%20on%2C%20money%20laundering%20etc.%2C%20because%20it%E2%80%99s%20big%20money.%20Poppy%20cultivation%2C%20the%20cultivation%20by%20the%20farmers%20is%20what%3F%20Maybe%205%25%20of%20the%20total%20drug%20trade.%20So%20the%20poppy%20cultivation%20itself%20is%20small%2C%20but%20there%20is%20a%20large%20inflow%20of%20drugs%20and%20chemicals%20coming%20across.%20And%20it%E2%80%99s%20partly%20because%20again%2C%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20realise%E2%80%A6%20because%20mainstream%20media%20in%20India%20has%20not%20covered%20a%20civil%20war%20which%20is%20going%20on%20in%20Myanmar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20mean%2C%20they%E2%80%99ve%20been%2C%20you%20know%E2%80%A6.%20we%E2%80%99ve%20had%20coverage%20once%2C%20in%20the%201960s%2C%20the%20air%20raid%20on%20Aizawl%2C%20those%20big%20headlines%E2%80%A6%20that%20%5Bthe%20air%20force%20was%5D%20used%20against%20their%20own%20citizens.%20The%20Myanmar%20government%20is%20bombing%20away%20left%2C%20right%20and%20centre%2C%20and%20therefore%2C%20you%20are%20going%20to%20have%20these%20refugees%20coming%20in%20to%20India.%20And%20I%20think%20it%20is%20very%20important%20for%20the%20government%20of%20India%20to%20have%2C%20if%20not%20a%20refugee%20policy%2C%20at%20least%20keep%20a%20complete%20tab%20on%20who%20is%20coming%20across%20the%20border%20and%20put%20them%20into%20refugee%20camps.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20serious%20is%20the%20influx%20of%20illegal%20Kuki%20refugees%20from%20Myanmar%3F%20All%20the%20newspaper%20reports%20I%E2%80%99ve%20read%20suggest%20that%20a%20survey%20done%20by%20the%20Manipur%20government%20put%20the%20numbers%20that%20entered%20Manipur%20under%203%2C000.%20Something%20like%2045%2C000%20have%20gone%20to%20Mizoram.%20How%20worrying%20is%20an%20influx%20of%203%2C000%3F%20Or%20is%20it%20being%20exaggerated%20to%20point%20fingers%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESee%2C%20one%2C%20since%20the%20actual%20thing%20has%20not%20been%20done%2C%20I%20would%20be%20skeptical%20about%20the%20numbers.%20I%20think%2C%20the%20figures%20in%20Mizoram%20are%20slightly%20more%20than%2045%2C000%20etc%2C.%20Maybe%20%5Bin%20Manipur%5D%203%2C000%20is%20slightly%20on%20the%20lower%20side.%20It%20may%20be%20higher%2C%20maybe%2010%2C000%2C%20maybe%20more.%20But%20these%20are%20refugees.%20See%2C%20nobody%20likes%20to%20leave%20his%20village%20and%20come%20across%20just%20carrying%20whatever%20is%20on%20the%20back%20of%20their%20head%20to%20another%20place%20unless%20there%20dire%20straits%20on%20the%20other%20side.%20So%20it%20is%20important%20for%20you%20to%20say%20that%20these%20are%20refugees%2C%20like%20when%20you%20know%20Bangladesh%E2%80%A6%20they%20had%20a%20problem%20in%20East%20Pakistan%20and%20so%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E10%20million%20came.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E10%20million%20came.%20So%20we%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThere%E2%80%99s%20a%20problem.%E2%80%9D%20The%20refugee%20camps%20were%20set%20up%2C%20you%20document%20them%2C%20you%20fingerprint%20them%2C%20you%20photograph%20them%2C%20you%20can%20do%20all%20that%20you%20want%2C%20and%20they%20remain%20as%20documented%20refugees%20in%20refugee%20camps.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EYou%E2%80%99re%20saying%20a%20very%20important%20thing.%20These%20people%20who%E2%80%99ve%20come%2C%20whether%20they%E2%80%99re%20three%2C%20four%2C%20five%20or%20ten%20thousand%2C%20they%E2%80%99re%20refugees%20%E2%80%93%20they%20are%20fleeing%20from%20terror%20in%20Myanmar.%20Obviously%2C%20at%20some%20point%2C%20they%20want%20to%20go%20back%20to%20their%20home.%20But%20they%20are%20not%20people%20who%E2%80%99ve%20come%20to%20make%20a%20living%20forever%20in%20India.%20There%20is%20a%20distinction%20to%20be%20made%20between%20refugees%20from%20militant%20Myanmar%20terror%20and%20people%20who%20have%20come%20to%20make%20a%20home%20in%20India.%20They%E2%80%99re%20the%20first%2C%20not%20the%20second.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYes%20and%20therefore%20once%20you%20document%20these%20refugees%2C%20he%20never%20becomes%20an%20illegal%20migrant%20because%20he%20always%20remains%20a%20refugee.%20Then%20you%20have%20to%20take%20up%20with%20the%20government%20of%20Myanmar%20to%20send%20them%20back%20at%20some%20point%20of%20time%2C%20when%20the%20situation%20is%20%5Bfine%5D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBut%20something%20else%20flows%20from%20what%20you%E2%80%99re%20saying.%20I%E2%80%99m%20talking%20now%20both%20about%20what%20you%20said%20earlier%20about%20the%20poppy%20trade%20and%20also%20about%20these%20refugees.%20In%20both%20cases%2C%20the%20finger%20has%20been%20pointed%20almost%20exclusively%2C%20at%20the%20Kuki%2C%20but%20you%E2%80%99re%20saying%20both%20sides%20are%20involved%2C%20in%20the%20poppy%20trade%20and%20the%20drug%20trade%20%E2%80%93%20Brinda%E2%80%99s%20interview%20makes%20that%20clear%2C%20the%20involvement%20on%20the%20Meitei%20side%20goes%20all%20the%20way%20to%20the%20chief%20minister.%20And%20again%2C%20you%20are%20saying%2C%20as%20regards%20these%20refugees%2C%20they%E2%80%99re%20not%20coming%20to%20permanently%20settle%2C%20they%20are%20fleeing%20for%20fear%20of%20their%20lives%20and%20they%20want%20to%20go%20back%20one%20day.%20Again%2C%20the%20finger%20is%20pointed%20to%20the%20Kuki%2C%20and%20said%20you%E2%80%99re%20deliberately%20changing%20the%20demography%20%E2%80%93%20they%E2%80%99re%20not.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20don%E2%80%99t%20think%20the%20demography%20will%20change.%20We%20don%E2%80%99t%20see%20that%20numbers%20yet.%20But%20remember%2C%20all%20the%20time%20we%E2%80%99re%20talking%20of%20%E2%80%9CKukis%E2%80%9D%20but%20the%20Kukis%2C%20they%20are%20also%20the%20Zomis%2C%20they%20are%20the%20Chins%20%E2%80%93%20all%20are%20different.%20I%20mean%20we%20look%20at%20it%E2%80%A6%20the%20Kuki%20is%20not%20the%20same%20as%20the%20Zo%20and%20the%20Chins.%20They%20fought%2C%20you%20know%2C%20in%20the%20late%2090s%2C%20the%20Kukis%20and%20the%20Paites%2C%20they%20had%20a%20huge%20fight%20where%2C%20you%20know%2C%20thousands%20were%20killed.%20So%20we%20have%20to%20see%20that%20different%20ethnic%20tribes%20from%20across%20the%20border%20are%20coming.%20Whether%20some%20of%20them%20are%20also%20involved%20in%20the%20drug%20trade%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20matter%20for%E2%80%A6%20its%20open.%20And%20if%20I%20am%20coming%20here%20and%20I%20am%2C%20shall%20I%20say%20not%20put%20in%20a%20refugee%20camp%2C%20where%20I%E2%80%99m%20housed%20as%20a%20UN%20High%20Commissioner%20for%20Refugees%2C%20they%20give%20you%20a%20refugee%20status%2C%20stamp%2C%20etc.%20Then%20you%20are%20on%20your%20own.%20And%20when%20you%20are%20on%20your%20own%2C%20I%20would%20not%20be%20surprised%20if%20some%20of%20them%20are%20also%20involved%20in%20this%20illegal%20drug%20trade%20because%20they%20will%20then%E2%80%A6%20they%20have%20to%20survive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIn%20other%20words%2C%20the%20administration%2C%20the%20system%20needs%20to%20respond%20more%20effectively%20to%20this%2C%20to%20ensure%20that%20refugees%20remain%20refugees.%20And%20this%20is%20again%20another%20area%20where%20the%20state%20administration%20has%20failed.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYeah%2C%20I%20think%20we%E2%80%99ve%20seen.%20Even%20in%20Mizoram%2C%20they%20are%20officially%20saying%20these%20are%20refugees.%20Some%20of%20them%20are%20housed%20in%20camps%2C%20some%20of%20them%20are%20housed%20with%20individual%20families%2C%20because%20they%E2%80%99re%2C%20you%20know%2C%20their%20relatives%2C%20their%20Chins%2C%20their%20communities%2C%20the%20same%20places%20and%20so%20on.%20But%20the%20government%20of%20India%20has%20not%20given%20a%20single%20pie%3Ci%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fi%3Eto%20the%20Mizoram%20government%20to%20help%20in%E2%80%A6%20the%20Mizoram%20government%20are%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CThese%20are%20the%20refugees%20who%20have%20come%20across%2C%20we%20got%20the%20names%20we%E2%80%99ve%20got%20this%20thing%2C%20we%20give%20you%20all%20%5Binformation%5D.%20We%20are%20providing%20funds%20from%20our%20state%20budget%2C%20help%20us%20with%20some%20money.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F11%2F11162601%2Frefugee-camp.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F11%2F11162601%2Frefugee-camp.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F11%2F11162601%2Frefugee-camp-300x198.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F11%2F11162601%2Frefugee-camp-1024x675.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-628160%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22791%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EFile%20image%3A%20A%20Zawlsei%20refugee%20camp%20in%20Mizoram%E2%80%99s%20Aizawl.%20The%20camp%20serves%20as%20home%20to%20Myanmarese%20who%20fled%20the%20military%20persecution%20in%20their%20country.%20Photo%3A%20Sushila%20Sahay%2FThe%20Wire%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Mizoram%20gov