20a%20forest%2C%20so%20there%20are%20some%20areas%20on%20which%20there%20is%20a%20little%20bit%20of%20a%20gray%20area.%20Those%20have%20not%20yet%20got%20implemented.%20Again%2C%20when%20the%20Manipur%20government%20starts%20to%20implement%20the%20new%20Forest%20Act%2C%20and%20declare%20a%20particular%20area%20as%20non-forest%20and%20so%20on%20and%20so%20forth%2C%20it%20will%20create%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAbsolutely%2C%20but%20this%20is%20the%20Manipur%20government%20again%20wrongly%20pointing%20fingers%20at%20the%20Kuki%20and%20claiming%20that%20they%E2%80%99re%20encroaching%2C%20when%20in%20fact%2C%20the%20government%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20understand%20the%20style%20of%20cultivation%20the%20Kukis%20use%3F%20Is%20there%20a%20mistake%20being%20made%20in%20pointing%20a%20finger%20at%20them%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESee%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20both.%20I%20think%20you%20have%20to%20look%20at%20the%20fact%20that%20there%20is%20one%20slash-and-burn%20cultivation%20which%20is%20normal.%20Then%2C%20you%20also%20have%20some%20encroachment%20which%20is%20taking%20place.%20People%20encroach%20anywhere%2C%20I%20mean%20it%E2%80%99s%20across%20the%20world%E2%80%A6.%20When%20any%20public%20area%20is%20available%E2%80%A6.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESo%20you%E2%80%99re%20suggesting%20that%20the%20charge%20of%20encroachment%20may%20not%20be%20wrong%20but%20it%E2%80%99s%20being%20exaggerated.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20think%20it%E2%80%99s%20been%20exaggerated%20but%20I%20would%20be%20surprised%20if%20there%20was%20not%20some%20encroachment%20into%20the%20forest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThat%E2%80%99s%20human%20nature%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHuman%20nature.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESo%20on%20the%20three%20background%20issues%20we%E2%80%99ve%20discussed%20%E2%80%93%20refugees%3B%20involvement%20in%20drug%20trade%20and%20poppy%20cultivation%3B%20and%20encroachment%20in%20forest%20areas%20%E2%80%93%20there%20is%20an%20element%20of%20exaggeration%20when%20the%20finger%20is%20pointed%20uniquely%20and%20exclusively%20at%20the%20Kuki.%20Both%20sides%20are%20involved%20in%20the%20drug%20trade.%20The%20refugees%20are%20actually%20refugees%2C%20they%E2%80%99re%20not%20coming%20to%20change%20the%20demography%20%E2%80%93%20they%20will%20go%20back%2C%20that%20needs%20to%20be%20understood.%20And%20as%20regards%20encroachment%2C%20there%20is%20some%20encroachment%20happening%20but%20it%E2%80%99s%20being%20exaggerated.%20Is%20that%20correct%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYes%2C%20I%20think%20that%E2%80%99s%20the%20actual%20ground%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELet%E2%80%99s%2C%20then%2C%20come%20to%20the%20two%20critical%20issues%2C%20that%20are%20perhaps%20the%20last%20part%20of%20this%20interview.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFrom%20the%20Meitei%20point%20of%20view%2C%20the%20real%20concern%20is%20what%20they%20call%20the%20%E2%80%9Cland%20imbalance%E2%80%9D.%20And%20they%20think%20it%20should%20be%20resolved%20in%20terms%20of%20giving%20them%20Scheduled%20Tribe%20(ST)%20status.%20Do%20you%20believe%20%E2%80%93%20given%20your%20understanding%20of%20Manipur%20and%20its%20complexities%20%E2%80%93%20that%20ST%20status%20is%20the%20right%20way%20of%20addressing%20the%20%E2%80%9Cland%20imbalance%E2%80%9D%3F%20Or%20are%20there%20other%20ways%20that%20could%20be%20equally%20efficacious%20but%20less%20controversial%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYes%2C%20I%20think%20so.%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20think%2C%20even%20among%20the%20Meiteis%E2%80%A6%20there%20was%20earlier%2C%20I%20think%20it%20was%20almost%2070%25%20of%20the%20Meiteis%20didn%E2%80%99t%20want%20ST%20status.%20Now%20they%20say%20it%E2%80%99s%20come%20to%2050-50%20after%20these%20clashes%20and%20so%20on.%20Land%20is%20an%20issue%2C%20no%20doubt%20about%20it.%20And%20the%20Meiteis%20have%20a%20genuine%20grievance%2C%20if%20I%20may%20put%20it%20that%20way.%20Primarily%2C%20again%20psychologically%2C%20that%20you%20know%20people%20from%20the%20hills%20can%20buy%20land%20in%20the%20valley%2C%20but%20you%20can%E2%80%99t%20buy%20land%20in%20the%20hills.%20And%20I%20think%20this%20is%20where%20I%20think%20political%20statesmanship%20from%20both%20sides%20involved%20%5Bis%20required%5D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20a%20certain%20land%20hunger%20there%20fore%20everybody.%20%5BIn%20the%20Valley%2C%5D%20it%20is%20very%20thickly%20populated%20and%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3Eless%20populated%20%5Bin%20the%20hills%5D%2C%20but%20of%20course%2C%20you%20also%20have%20forest%20areas..%20so%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20apple%20to%20apple.%20So%20you%20need%20some%20element%20of%20political%20compromise%20by%20which%20the%20Meiteis%20also%20can%20have%20some%20access%20to%20land%20in%20the%20hill%20areas%20for%20certain%20purposes.%20You%20can%20have%20a%20restriction%2C%20you%20can%20say%2C%20ceiling%20will%20be%205%25%20or%2010%25%20of%20the%20total%20area%20for%20A%2CB%2CC%20purposes%20etc%2C.%20Some%20of%20it%2C%20there%20have%20been%20discussions%20in%20the%20past%20with%20the%20Hill%20Area%20Council%20in%20terms%20of%20%E2%80%93%20for%20industrial%20purposes%2C%20for%20setting%20up%20industrial%20parks%20in%20the%20hill%20areas%3B%20for%20the%20Meiteis%20who%20come%20and%20settle%20down%2C%20who%20are%20working%20government%20servants.%20Under%20the%20Manipur%20Public%20Service%20Commission%2C%20they%20get%20recruited%2C%20then%20you%20can%20get%20them%20posted%20to%20the%20hills%2C%20you%20might%20marry%20somebody%20there%20and%20you%20want%20to%20settle%20down%20there.%20Then%20you%20should%20be%20allowed%20%5Bto%20buy%20land%5D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThat%20permission%20from%20hill%20councils%20is%20already%20available%20but%20it%2C%20I%20gather%2C%20is%20given%20very%20grudgingly.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYeah%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20given%20grudgingly%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20very%20little.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EYou%20are%20saying%20that%20this%20is%20an%20issue%2C%20the%20land%20imbalance%2C%20that%20with%20the%20political%20initiative%20taken%20by%20sensible%20farsighted%20politicians%20can%20be%20very%20easily%20reserved.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYes%2C%20people%20have%20to%20realise%20that%20it%20is%20an%20issue.%20You%20have%20to%20realise%20that%20the%20Meiteis%20have%20a%20problem.%20Don%E2%80%99t%20brush%20it%20aside%2C%20under%20the%20carpet.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20hills%20are%20ours%2C%20we%20are%20not%20going%20to%20give%20you%20a%20cent%20of%20it.%E2%80%9D%20I%20think%20you%20can%E2%80%99t%20take%20that%20attitude.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBut%20the%20corollary%2C%20you%E2%80%99re%20saying%20this%20can%20be%20resolved%20without%20necessarily%20giving%20the%20Meitei%20ST%20status.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIn%20other%20words%2C%20you%20need%20a%20far-sighted%20politician%20who%20takes%20the%20initiative.%20And%20that%20means%20someone%20has%20to%20stick%20their%20neck%20out%2C%20because%20that%E2%80%99s%20what%20you%20do%20when%20you%20take%20an%20initiative%2C%20isn%E2%80%99t%20it%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYeah%2C%20I%20think%20a%20lot%20of%20Meiteis%E2%80%A6%20a%20lot%20of%20responsible%20citizens%20also%20say%20that%20the%20current%20definition%20of%20STs%20does%20not%20apply%20to%20the%20Meiteis.%20Some%20of%20them%20are%20Vaishnavite%20Brahmins%3B%20some%20of%20them%2C%20of%20course%2C%20looking%20back%20to%20their%20old%20indigenous%20faith%2C%20in%20which%20case%2C%20they%20are%2C%20you%20know%2C%20shall%20have%20more%20akin%20to%20STs.%20But%20today%2C%20in%20the%20context%20of%20where%20they%20are%20now%2C%20in%20terms%20of%20their%20education%2C%20their%20social%20position%2C%20lack%20of%20discrimination%2C%20nobody%20discriminates%20against%20Meiteis%3B%20the%20educational%20levels%E2%80%A6%20All%20the%20things%20which%20ST%20commission%20would%20actually%20look%20at%20to%20see%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA