d%20that%20after%20what%20they%E2%80%99ve%20gone%20through%2C%20the%20Kuki%20clearly%20want%20some%20measure%20of%20autonomy%20to%20be%20able%20to%20safeguard%20themselves.%20So%20how%20would%20you%2C%20if%20you%20were%20home%20secretary%20now%2C%20tackle%20this%20extremely%20difficult%20situation%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESee%20I%E2%80%99ve%20always%20been%20of%20the%20view%20that%E2%80%A6%20and%20in%20fact%2C%20as%20joint%20secretary%20(northeast)%2C%20there%E2%80%99s%20even%20a%20literally%2C%20an%20affidavit%20of%20mine%20in%20the%20Manipur%20assembly%2C%20saying%20that%20the%20government%20of%20India%20is%20committed%20to%20the%20territorial%20integrity%20of%20Manipur.%20I%E2%80%99ve%20said%20that%20even%20during%20the%20Naga%20talks%20and%20so%20on%20%E2%80%93%20we%20are%20not%20touching%20that.%20If%20you%20are%20not%20touching%20that%2C%20then%20the%20issue%20then%20becomes%20a%20matter%20of%20autonomy.%20You%20got%20the%20Hill%20Areas%20Council%2C%20which%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20really%20worked%20because%20again%20the%20state%E2%80%A6%20no%20state%20government%20likes%20to%20give%20autonomy.%20It%E2%80%99s%20happened%20in%20Assam%20when%20you%20had%20Sixth%20Schedule%20status%20and%20even%20the%20Sixth%20Schedule%20areas.%20When%20we%20negotiated%20the%20Bodo%20Accord%2C%20we%20gave%20a%20lot%20of%20autonomy%20but%20they%20still%20feel%20that%20because%20the%20money%20is%20routed%20through%20the%20state%20government%2C%20who%20controls%20the%20money%2C%20controls%20everything%20else.%20So%20unless%20there%20is%20financial%20autonomy%2C%20it%20becomes%20very%20difficult%20for%20anybody%20to%20feel%20that%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99m%20really%20autonomous.%E2%80%9D%20Therefore%2C%20an%20autonomous%20council%2C%20an%20autonomous%20area%20is%20fine.%20It%20can%20be%20under%20the%20Sixth%20Schedule.%20I%20think%2C%20in%20the%20past%2C%20even%20in%20Manipur%20there%E2%80%99s%20been%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBut%20the%20Sixth%20Schedule%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20apply%20to%20Manipur.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%2C%20it%20can%20be.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIt%20can%20be%20applied.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20can%20be%20extended%20to%20any%20particular%20area%20which%20the%20government%20wants.%20In%20the%20past%2C%20Manipur%20governments%20have%20said%20that%20this%20is%20acceptable%20but%20this%20is%20something%20to%20be%20negotiated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThere%20are%20reports%20in%20the%20papers%20that%20the%20talks%20that%20were%20happening%20with%20the%20SoO%20%5BSuspension%20of%20Operations%5D%20groups%20and%20the%20home%20ministry%20%E2%80%93%20which%20then%20got%20overtaken%2C%20when%20May%203%20happened%20%E2%80%93%20were%20reaching%20a%20sort%20of%20conclusion.%20Reports%20suggest%20the%20SoO%20groups%20were%20willing%20to%20concede%20that%20autonomous%20hill%20area%20councils%20or%20autonomous%20territorial%20councils%20%E2%80%93%20perhaps%20under%20the%20Sixth%20Schedule%20%E2%80%93%20would%20be%20acceptable.%20Now%2C%20the%20Kuki%20say%20that%20the%20door%20is%20closed.%20Do%20you%20think%20it%20can%20be%20reopened%3F%20Can%20this%20package%20be%20sweetened%20to%20make%20the%20Kuki%20accept%20it%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20think%20it%20can%20be%20reopened.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20question%20of%E2%80%A6%20you%20have%20to%20give%20it%20a%20little%20bit%20of%20time.%20I%20think%20you%20have%20to%20allow%20the%20other%20processes%20which%20I%20mentioned%20earlier%E2%80%A6%20the%20step-by-step%20processes%20in%20terms%20of%20law%20and%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAnd%20leave%20this%20to%20the%20last.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20leave%20this%20to%20a%20couple%20of%20years%20down%20the%20line.%20Because%2C%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20think%20at%20this%20stage%2C%20anything%E2%80%A6%20forget%20Sixth%20Schedule%2C%20forget%20UT%2C%20forget%20a%20new%20state%2C%20etc.%2C%20will%20be%20discussed%20at%20all.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20just%20too%20early.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20too%20early%2C%20so%20that%E2%80%99s%20two-three%20years%20down%20the%20line%2C%20as%20I%20put%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBut%20you%E2%80%99re%20also%20suggesting%20that%20to%20make%20the%20hill%20area%20councils%20or%20the%20autonomous%20territorial%20districts%20or%20whatever%20you%20call%20them%20acceptable%2C%20you%E2%80%99d%20have%20to%20also%20apply%20the%20Sixth%20Schedule%20of%20the%20constitution%20%E2%80%93%20so%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20lot%20closer%20to%20the%20Bodoland%20structure.%20And%20perhaps%2C%20in%20addition%2C%20give%20them%20also%20some%20measure%20of%20financial%20autonomy.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYeah%2C%20that%20is%2C%20those%20are%20parts%20which%20can%20be%20negotiated%20with%20over%20a%20period%E2%80%A6%20I%20put%20it%20as%20I%20think%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20about%20two%20three-years%20down%20the%20line%2C%20when%20all%20other%20things%E2%80%A6%20As%20I%20said%2C%20I%E2%80%99m%20hoping%20that%20slowly%20all%20the%20other%20positive%20steps%20will%20take%20place%2C%20and%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%2C%20and%20this%20is%20my%20great%20fear%2C%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%E2%80%A6%20I%20think%20for%20two-three%20months%2C%20I%20think%20by%20November-December%2C%20I%20think%20there%E2%80%99ll%20be%20relative%20calm.%20But%20there%20is%20a%20lurking%20fear%20that%20you%20might%20again%20end%20up%20with%20another%20burst%20of%20violence.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20do%20you%20say%20till%20November-December%E2%80%A6%20What%20worries%20you%20after%20that%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20umber%20of%20issues.%20From%20one%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20looking%20at%20the%20whole%20issue%2C%20there%20are%20some%20issues%20which%20are%20taking%20place%E2%80%A6%20the%20poppy%20cultivation%20gets%20harvested%20in%20November%2C%20so%20nobody%20wants%E2%80%A6%20Both%20sides%2C%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20anything%20which%20might%20affect%20the%20cultivation%20of%20poppy.%20So%20many%20issues%20are%20there%20on%20the%20back%20of%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIf%20I%20understand%20correctly%2C%20what%20you%E2%80%99re%20saying%20is%20that%20both%20sides%20have%20an%20interest%20in%20ensuring%20that%20the%20poppy%20harvest%20is%20not%20affected.%20Both%20sides%20have%20an%20interest%20in%20watching%20to%20see%20how%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20reacts%2C%20which%20is%20why%20there%20will%20be%20a%20sense%20of%20relative%20calm%20until%20November-December.%20Your%20worry%20is%20once%20the%20poppy%20harvest%20is%20done%20and%20once%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20perhaps%2C%20turned%20its%20attention%20to%20other%20matters%2C%20the%20situation%20can%20flare%20up%20again%2C%20around%20November-December.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhich%20is%20why%20I%20mentioned%20that%2C%20you%20know%2C%20the%20earlier%20steps%20like%20recovery%20of%20all%20looted%20arms%3B%20getting%20the%20administration%20in%20these%20areas%20back%3B%20%5Bearning%20the%5D%20trust%20of%20the%20people%3B%20you%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20too%20many%20sporadic%20issues%20which%20keep%20tension%20rising%3B%20%C2%A0but%20there%20is%20a%20sort%20of%20gradual%20calming%E2%80%A6%20people%20feel%20things%20are%20back%20to%20normal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThose%20are%20critical%20steps.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThose%20are%20critical%20steps%2C%20because%20otherwise%2C%20if%20you%20have%203%2C000-4%2C000%20arms%20%E2%80%93%20maybe%20more%2C%20which%20come%20in%20from%20across%20the%20border%20and%20so%20on%20%E2%80%93%20you%20are%20sitting%20on%20a%20tinder%20box%20which%20you%20have%20to%20be%20very%20careful%20%E2%80%93%20can%20always%20blow%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBut%20the%20problem%20is%20those%20critical%20steps%20are%20not%20happening.%20We%E2%80%99ve%20discussed%20them%20in%20detail%2C%20but%