20shrine%20is%20a%20symbol%20of%20communal%20harmony%20in%20the%20town%20where%20Hindus%20live%20in%20majority.%20Kishtwar%20has%20witnessed%20some%20of%20the%20deadliest%20riots%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20many%20of%20them%20timed%20to%20set%20the%20tone%20for%20polarisation%20ahead%20of%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20because%20of%20the%20saint%E2%80%99s%20blessing%20that%20Muslims%20and%20Hindus%20of%20Kishtwar%20continue%20to%20live%20in%20harmony.%20There%20have%20been%20many%20ugly%20communal%20incidents%20but%20the%20two%20communities%20have%20sorted%20them%20out%20amicably%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Shan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGupta%2C%2055%2C%20a%20BJP%20supporter%2C%20believes%20that%20his%20Hindu%20faith%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20forbid%20him%20from%20visiting%20Shah%20Asrar%E2%80%99s%20shrine%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20don%E2%80%99t%20stop%20my%20Muslim%20workers%20when%20they%20want%20to%20offer%20prayers.%20All%20religions%20teach%20us%20tolerance%20and%20respect%20for%20others.%20Politics%20has%20divided%20us%20but%20Asrar%20saheb%20continues%20to%20unite%20us.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693481421000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F31133327%2FIMG_4844.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fjk-kishtwars-sufi-shrine-unites-muslims-hindus-stands-tall-as-symbol-of-communal-harmony%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Although%20Kishtwar%20has%20seen%20deadly%20communal%20riots%20in%20the%20recent%20past%20ahead%20of%20elections%2C%20people%20of%20all%20faiths%20in%20this%20mountainous%20district%20celebrate%20annual%20festival%20of%20Shah%20Asrar%2C%20a%2017-century%20Sufi%20saint%2C%20after%20whom%20the%20shrine%20is%20named.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fjk-kishtwars-sufi-shrine-unites-muslims-hindus-stands-tall-as-symbol-of-communal-harmony%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20India's%20Leadership%20Of%20The%20Global%20South%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndia's%20stature%20as%20a%20strong%20and%20influential%20nation%20on%20the%20global%20stage%20has%20grown%20markedly%20in%20the%20last%2010%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20interview%20with%20NDTV%2C%20External%20Affairs%20Minister%20S%20Jaishankar%20said%20India's%20G20%20presidency%20has%20been%20unique%20and%20special%20in%20a%20world%20that%20is%20far%20more%20complicated%20because%20of%20a%20once-in-a-century%20pandemic%20and%20an%20ongoing%20conflict.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20such%20a%20situation%2C%20who%20can%20step%20forward%20and%20find%20a%20middle%20ground%3F%20There%20are%20east-west%20and%20north-south%20divides.%20Who%20can%20bridge%20this%3F%20The%20country%20should%20not%20be%20neutral%2C%20but%20command%20respect%20and%20have%20something%20to%20show%20to%20the%20world.%20That%20is%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20Foreign%20Minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20emerged%20as%20a%20trustworthy%20and%20dependable%20leader%20of%20the%20countries%20of%20the%20Global%20South%20and%20has%20also%20displayed%20its%20collaborative%20spirit%20by%20reaching%20out%20to%20125%20countries%20to%20co-create%20the%20G20%20agenda%20during%20its%20presidency.%20A%20two-day%20virtual%20meet%20of%20the%20Global%20South%20countries%20was%20organised%20in%20January.%20India%20initiated%20the%20idea%20of%20granting%20permanent%20status%20to%20the%20African%20Union%20to%20become%20a%20member%20of%20the%20G20.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20lot%20was%20expected%20from%20China%2C%20which%20has%20been%20claiming%20to%20advocate%20the%20cause%20of%20the%20Global%20South%20but%20in%20reality%2C%20has%20been%20acting%20in%20strange%20ways%20through%20policies%20like%20the%20BRI%20(Belt%20and%20Road%20Initiative)%20and%20the%20notorious%20%26quot%3Bdebt%20trap%26quot%3B%20for%20nations%20seeking%20funds.%20Over%20two%20dozen%20countries%20in%20Asia%20and%20Africa%20are%20victims%20of%20China's%20bullying.%20As%20part%20of%20BRI%2C%20there%20are%20many%20cases%20of%20countries%20losing%20possession%20of%20assets%20like%20Hambantota%20port%20in%20Sri%20Lanka%2C%20Mombasa%20port%20in%20Kenya%2C%20several%20areas%20in%20Pakistan%2C%20Tajikistan%2C%20and%20Kyrgyzstan.%20The%20Chinese%20image%20has%20taken%20a%20beating%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Srikanth%20Kondapalli%2C%20Dean%2C%20School%20of%20International%20Studies%2C%20JNU.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20been%20resolutely%20championing%20the%20cause%20of%20Global%20South%2C%20as%20much%20as%20its%20own%20problems.%20The%20Foreign%20Minister%20explained%20the%20spirit%20of%20the%20Global%20South%20as%20countries%20who%2C%20with%20their%20limited%20resources%2C%20will%20do%20for%20other%20countries%20what%20they%20will%20do%20to%20solve%20their%20own%20problems.%20Citing%20it%20as%20a%20family%20unit%2C%20he%20placed%20India%20in%20that%20category.%20India's%20success%20with%20the%20Chandrayaan%20has%20been%20celebrated%20the%20world%20over%20and%20many%20nations%20in%20the%20Global%20South%20have%20basked%20in%20the%20reflected%20glory%20of%20this%20achievement%2C%20which%20is%20an%20example%20of%20this%20familial%20spirit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20presidency%20year%2C%20India%20highlighted%20and%20made%20concerted%20efforts%20to%20address%20economic%20challenges%20like%20the%20crippling%20food%20and%20energy%20crisis%20due%20to%20the%20ongoing%20Ukraine%20war.%20The%20export%20of%20wheat%2C%20hampered%20due%20to%20the%20ongoing%20war%2C%20has%20aggravated%20the%20food%20crisis%20in%20many%20countries.%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20as%20a%20solution%2C%20propounded%20the%20merits%20of%20millets%20-%20the%20healthy%2C%20green%20and%20better%20substitute%20of%20wheat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeveloped%20countries%20have%20tasted%20China's%20economic%20coercion%20in%20the%20form%20of%20trade%20embargoes%20and%20sanctions.%20After%20Australia%20last%20year%20called%20for%20an%20international%20investigation%20into%20the%20outbreak%20of%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%2C%20Beijing%20responded%20with%20a%20barrage%20of%20tariffs%20and%20restrictions%20on%20its%20exports.%20The%20world%20has%20seen%20the%20fragility%20of%20global%20supply%20chains%20during%20Covid%20and%20the%20Russia-Ukraine%20war.%20The%20pandemic%20and%20post-pandemic%20disruptions%20to%20the%20supply%20chain%20have%20diminished%20China's%20appeal.%20To%20reduce%20their%20strategic%20vulnerabilities%2C%20foreign%20investors%20are%20looking%20for%20alternative%20destinations%20to%20shift%20their%20manufacturing%20locations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Foreign%20Minister%20says%20India%20can%20fill%20the%20gap%20as%20he%20feels%20manufacturing%20is%20over-concentrated%20in%20China%20and%20a%20situation%20like%20a%20pandemic%20can%20disrupt%20economies.%20%26quot%3BIndia%20has%20an%20advantage%20as%20its%20quality%20of%20soft%20power%20is%20better%20than%20China.%20Indeed%2C%20in%20the%20post-Covid%20scenario%20followed%20by%20China's%20belligerent%20foreign%20policy%2C%20the%20world%20wants%20to%20manufacture%20in%20India.%20India%20now%20has%20the%20opportunity%20to%20pitch%20itself%20as%20the%20next%20factory-of-the%20world.%20Unlike%20many%20competitors%2C%20India%20has%20the%20capacity%2C%20skills%2C%20low%20production%20costs%20and%20the%20scalability%20to%20make-in-India%20for%20the%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Atul%20Aneja%2C%20editor-India%20Narrative%2C%20formerly%20China%20correspondent%20(The%20Hindu).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%2C%20riding%20on%20its%20advancement%20in%20technology%20(even%20the%20West%20benefits%20from%20India's%20strong%20digital%20talent)%2C%20high%20demographic%20dividend%2C%20and%20large%20consumer%20market%2C%20is%20perceived%20as%20the%20counterweight%20to%20China.%20The%20western%20world%20also%20has%20been%20trying%20to%20counter%20China%20by%20manifesting%20a%20tilt%20towards%20India.%20%26quot%3BIt%20means%20that%20the%20world%20is%20not%20decoupling%20but%20de-risking%20from%20China%2C%20by%20forging%20alternative%20supply%20chains%20and%20manufacturing.%20India%20is%20well-poised%20to%20benefit%20from%20this%20post-Covid%20global%20strategy%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Mr%20Aneja.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20a%20huge%20domestic%20market%20of%201.4%20billion%20people%2C%20and%20an%20expanding%20middle%20class%20with%20growing%20purchasing%20power.%20In%20the%20last%2010%20years%2C%20India%20has%20progressed%20considerably.%20We%20have%20a%20large%20pool%20of%20skilled%20and%20educated%20people%20who%20are%20employable%20across%20sectors%2C%20from%20technology%2C%20manufacturing%20to%20healthcare%2C%20services%20and%20heavy%20engineering.%20Indian%20has%20a%20thriving%20entrepreneurial%20ecosystem%20with%20a%20mix%20of%20start-ups%20and%20established%20companies%20across%20various%20industries.%20These%20start-ups%20predominantly%20serve%20global%20clients%2C%20underscoring%20that%20the%20nation%20is%20no%20longer%20viewed%20solely%20as%20a%20hug%20for%20(low-cost)%20labour%20arbitrage%2C%20but%20as%20a%20pivotal%20destination%20for%20value-addition%20in%20the%20life%20cycle%20of%20global%20corporations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20our%20young%20population%20of%20below%2035%20will%20continue%20to%20yield%20demographic%20dividends%20to%20our%20advantage%2C%20unlike%20China%2C%20which%20will%20soon%20be%20short%20of%20a%20young%2C%20employable%20workforce.%20Mr%20Jaishankar's%20comment%20on%20the%20strong%20link%20between%20jobs%20creation%2C%20infrastructure%20growth%20and%20ensuring%20private%20capital%20from%20abroad%20can%20easily%20access%20manufacturing%20opportunities%20in%20the%20domestic%20market%2C%20stands%20true%20in%20this%20context.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20WEF%20(World%20Economic%20Forum)%20report%20states%20that%20one%20of%20the%20countries%20most%20likely%20to%20benefit%20in%20South%20Asia%20is%20India%20because%20it%20attracted%20among%20the%20highest%20FDIs%20at%20%2483.6%20billion%20in%20the%20financial%20year%202021-22.%20In%20terms%20of%20market%20and%20cost%20effectiveness%2C%20India%20is%20as%20lucrative%20as%20the%20US%20or%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20is%20on%20the%20verge%20of%20emerging%20as%20a%20market%20leader%20in%20specific%20sectors%2C%20notably%20in%20the%20critical%20domain%20of%20renewable%20energy%2C%20in%20which%20the%20country%20is%20poised%20to%20become%20the%20largest%20solar%20energy%20producer%20in%20the%20world.%20Green%20transportation%2C%20and%20green%20mobility%20were%20the%20other%20areas%20of%20focus%20for%20India%2C%20as%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20said.%20To%20lessen%20the%20country's%20dependence%20on%20China%2C%20the%20government%20has%20cleared%20a%2010-billion-dollar%20package%20to%20boost%20the%20semiconductor%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20India%20is%20grappling%20with%20major%20challenges.%20Ease%20of%20doing%20business%2C%20eliminating%20red%20tape%2C%20labour%20law%20reforms%2C%20objective%20tax%20regime%2C%20better%20infrastructure%20to%20cater%20to%20supply%20chains%2C%20and%20global%20work%20and%20living%20standards%2C%20are%20areas%20needing%20urgent%20attention.%20%26quot%3BIndia%20has%20two%20main%20problems%20-%20one%20is%20massive%20red%20tape%20and%20corruption%2C%20and%20two%2C%20poor%20quality%20skills%20of%20labour.%20Surely%2C%20India%20will%20attract%20investment%20more%20to%20cater%20to%20the%20domestic%20market%20than%20become%20a%20manufacturing%20hub%20for%20exports%20as%20China%20did%20for%20nearly%20four%20decades.%20So%2C%20despite%20all%20the%20hype%2C%20one%20should%20be%20realistic.%20That%20Japan%2C%20India's%20Special%20Strategic%20Partner%2C%20has%20been%20investing%20more%20in%20Vietnam%20than%20in%20India%2C%20gives%20an%20idea%20about%20what's%20happening%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20GVC%20Naidu%2C%20former%20founder%20chairperson%2C%20Centre%20for%20Indo-Pacific%20Studies%2C%20JNU.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20world%20is%20keen%20to%20support%20a%20strong%20democracy%20as%20a%20viable%20business%20alternative.%20The%20West%20is%20experiencing%20what%20is%20to%20be%20on%20the%20receiving%20end%20of%20China's%20bullying%20behaviour.%20India%20must%20not%20waste%20this%20opportunity.%20It's%20a%20large%20country%20with%20transparent%20and%20strong%20democratic%20institutions.%20India%20should%20not%20be%20seen%20as%20China%20Plus%20One%2C%20as%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20says.%20Definitely%20not%2C%20when%20its%20growth%20has%20been%20cushioned%20by%20domestic%20consumption%20despite%20the%20global%20slowdown.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Bharti%20Mishra%20Nath%20is%20a%20senior%20journalist)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693481340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-11%2F8gv2lcs8_pm-modi-at-g20_625x300_16_November_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Findias-leadership-of-the-global-south-4345410%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India's%20stature%20as%20a%20strong%20and%20influential%20nation%20on%20the%20global%20stage%20has%20grown%20markedly%20in%20the%20last%2010%20years.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Findias-leadership-of-the-global-south-4345410%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Findias-leadership-of-the-global-south-4345410%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Findias-leadership-of-the-global-south-4345410%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Vistara%20to%20begin%202nd%20Thiruvananthapuram-Mumbai%20flight%20service%20from%20Sep%201%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693481323000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2020-12%2F07%2Ffull%2F1607307191-9678.