0being%20called%20from%2018th%20to%2022nd%20September%20having%205%20sittings.%C2%A0%20Amid%20Amrit%20Kaal%20looking%20forward%20to%20have%20fruitful%20discussions%20and%20debate%20in%20Parliament%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3ESpecial%20Session%20of%20Parliament%20(13th%20Session%20of%2017th%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20261st%20Session%20of%20Rajya%20Sabha)%20is%20being%20called%20from%2018th%20to%2022nd%20September%20having%205%20sittings.%20Amid%20Amrit%20Kaal%20looking%20forward%20to%20have%20fruitful%20discussions%20and%20debate%20in%20Parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E0%B2%B8%E0%B2%82%E0%B2%B8%E0%B2%A4%E0%B3%8D%E0%B2%A4%E0%B2%BF%E0%B2%A8%20%E0%B2%B5%E0%B2%BF%E0%B2%B6%E0%B3%87%E0%B2%B7%20%E0%B2%85%E0%B2%A7%E0%B2%BF%E0%B2%B5%E0%B3%87%E0%B2%B6%E0%B2%A8%E0%B2%B5%E0%B2%A8%E0%B3%8D%E0%B2%A8%E0%B3%81%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Fk5J2PA1wv2%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2Fk5J2PA1wv2%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Pralhad%20Joshi%20(%40JoshiPralhad)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FJoshiPralhad%2Fstatus%2F1697184544489910439%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EAugust%2031%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20there%20is%20no%20word%20on%20what%20the%20agenda%20will%20be%20for%20the%20five-day%20session%20which%20is%20scheduled%20days%20after%20the%20G20%20summit%20in%20New%20Delhi%20on%20September%209%20and%2010%20%E2%80%93%20and%20just%20weeks%20after%20the%20monsoon%20session%20of%20parliament%20concluded%20on%20August%2011.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20said%20that%20the%20session%20could%20offer%20the%20government%20an%20opportunity%20to%20showcase%20the%20success%20of%20the%20G20%20summit%20and%20set%20the%20stage%20for%20the%20%E2%80%9CP20%20summit%E2%80%9D.%20The%20Parliament20%20(P20)%20Engagement%20Group%2C%20started%20during%20Canada%E2%80%99s%20G20%20Pr