reported.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''If%20you%20go%20dancing%20you%20are%20fully%20entitled%20to%20get%20drunk%20...%20but%20if%20you%20avoid%20getting%20drunk%20and%20losing%20consciousness%2C%20perhaps%20you'd%20also%20avoid%20getting%20into%20trouble%20because%20then%20you'll%20find%20the%20wolf%2C''%20Andrea%20Giambruno%20said%20on%20his%20show%20on%20channel%20Rete%204%20while%20discussing%20recent%20gang-rapes%20in%20the%20country.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20show%2C%20he%20also%20agreed%20with%20the%20editor%20of%20the%20rightwing%20Libero%20newspaper%2C%20Pietro%20Senaldi%2C%20who%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CIf%20you%20want%20to%20avoid%20rape%2C%20above%20all%20don't%20lose%20consciousness%2C%20keep%20your%20wits%20about%20you.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20opinion%20has%20now%20sparked%20political%20outrage%20in%20Italy%2C%20as%20well%20as%20a%20row%20on%20social%20media.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''They%20just%20can't%20help%20but%20blame%20women.%20Don't%20go%20out%20alone%2C%20don't%20go%20where%20it's%20dark%2C%20don't%20dress%20provocatively.%20All%20this%20is%20no%20longer%20acceptable%2C''%20said%20Cecilia%20D'Elia%2C%20a%20senator%20with%20the%20opposition%20Partito%20Democratico.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20data-testid%3D%5C%22paragraph-4%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20a%20girl%20drinks%20too%20much%2C%20she%20can%20expect%20a%20headache%2C%20not%20a%20rape%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20opposition%20Five%20Star%20Movement%20party%20(M5S)%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20that%20%E2%80%9CGiambruno's%20words%20are%20unacceptable%20and%20shameful%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cthey%20represent%20a%20male-dominated%20and%20retrograde%20culture%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20data-testid%3D%5C%22paragraph-4%5C%22%3EHowever%2C%20Mr%C2%A0Giambruno%20denied%20victim%20blaming%20and%20said%20his%20comments%20had%20been%20taken%20out%20of%20context%2C%20reported%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-66657267%5C%22%3EBBC%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E.%20%26quot%3BI%20never%20said%20men%20are%20free%20to%20rape%20women%20who%20are%20drunk%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20explained%2C%20adding%20that%20he%20had%20prefaced%20his%20remarks%20by%20stressing%20that%20it%20was%20an%20%26quot%3Babominable%20act%20carried%20out%20by%20beasts%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20I%20had%20said%20something%20wrong%2C%20I%20would%20have%20apologised%2C%20but%20that's%20not%20the%20case%20and%20there%20will%20never%20be%20a%20day%20when%20a%20politician%20tells%20me%20what%20to%20say.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20said%20rape%20is%20an%20abominable%20act.%20I%20took%20the%20liberty%20of%20telling%20young%20people%20not%20to%20go%20out%20on%20purpose%20to%20get%20drunk%20and%20do%20drugs.%20I%20advised%20them%20to%20be%20careful%20because%2C%20unfortunately%2C%20the%20bad%20guys%20are%20always%20out%20there.%20I%20never%20said%20that%20men%20are%20entitled%20to%20rape%20drunk%20women.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20data-testid%3D%5C%22paragraph-4%5C%22%3EMr%20Giambruno%20has%20a%20seven-year-old%20daughter%20with%20Prime%20Minister%20Meloni.%20Meanwhile%2C%20the%20PM%20has%20not%20yet%20commented%20on%20the%20recent%20rapes%20or%20her%20partner's%20statements.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693480860000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Ff5mem5q_-andrea-giambruno_625x300_31_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Favoid-getting-drunk-italy-pms-partner-faces-backlash-for-rape-comments-4345347%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22While%20commenting%20on%20the%20gang-rape%20of%20a%20woman%2C%20TV%20presenter%20Andrea%20Giambruno%2C%20said%20women%20could%20avoid%20sexual%20assaults%20if%20they%20''do%20not%20get%20too%20drunk''.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Favoid-getting-drunk-italy-pms-partner-faces-backlash-for-rape-comments-4345347%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22