0happening%20and%20said%20nowhere%20in%20Western%20Russia%20will%20be%20safe.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ESome%20strikes%20have%20destroyed%20Russian%20aircraft%2C%20and%20one%20blogger%20was%20angry%20Russia%20couldn't%20protect%20them.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ERussia's%20nationalists%20are%20fuming%20over%20a%20slew%20of%20attacks%20on%20Russian%20territory%20which%20exposed%20gaps%20in%20its%20defenses%20and%20put%20it%20on%20the%20back%20foot%20in%20its%20invasion%20of%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20hardliners%20criticized%20Russia's%20leaders%20for%20what%20they%20called%20their%20failure%20to%20protect%20the%20country.%20They%20also%20accused%20them%20of%20covering%20up%20the%20extent%20of%20new%20attacks%20hitting%20Russia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20blowback%20was%20picked%20up%20by%20the%20respected%20Institute%20for%20the%20Study%20of%20War%20think%20tank%2C%20which%20described%20it%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.iswresearch.org%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ein%20an%20update%20on%20Wednesday%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20ISW%20wrote%20that%20%26quot%3BRussian%20propagandists%20and%20milbloggers%20criticized%20Russian%20forces%20for%20their%20inability%20to%20defend%20Russian%20territory%20and%20military%20facilities%2C%20while%20simultaneously%20criticizing%20recent%20Russian%20MoD%20censorship%20efforts.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20highlighted%20Telegram%20posts%20by%20popular%20media%20figures%20in%20Russia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Frybar%2F51327%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20prominent%20anonymous%20blogger%20Rybar%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20a%20recent%20strike%20on%20Russia's%20Pskov%20airfield%20suggests%20Russia's%20air%20defenses%20haven't%20adapted%20to%20stop%20drone%20strikes.%20It%20criticized%20authorities%20for%20not%20protecting%20the%20valuable%20aircraft%20there%20with%20hangars%2C%20and%20compared%20their%20defenses%20unfa