0months%20because%20of%20a%20slump%20in%20global%20demand%20and%20reduced%20domestic%20consumer%20spending.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jwilkins%40insider.com%20(Joseph%20Wilkins)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A8%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchinas-manufacturing-sector-contracts-for-the-fifth-consecutive-month-economy-2023-8%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22G20%20Summit%20FAQs%3A%20How%20To%20Reach%20Airport%2C%20Stations%3F%20Will%20Metro%20Be%20Available%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20G20%20summit%20begins%20in%20Delhi%20early%20next%20month%20and%20the%20traffic%20police%20has%20released%20detailed%20guidelines%20on%20the%20arrangements%20put%20in%20place%20for%20the%20movement%20of%20traffic%20in%20the%20national%20capital.%20The%20gathering%20of%20the%20heads%20of%20state%20and%20other%20dignitaries%20will%20be%20held%20on%20September%209%20and%2010%20at%20the%20newly-built%20Bharat%20Mandapam%20at%20Pragati%20Maidan.%20Authorities%20have%20closed%20all%20the%20markets%2C%20banks%20and%20other%20commercial%20establishments%20in%20the%20areas%20around%20Pragati%20Maidan.%20Since%20large%20parts%20of%20New%20Delhi%20will%20be%20out%20of%20bounds%2C%20the%20traffic%20police%20has%20explained%20how%20people%20can%20commute%20during%20that%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Fg20-summit-dos-and-donts-and-whats-open-whats-closed-in-delhi-4335799%5C%22%3EG20%20Summit%3A%20Dos%20And%20Dont's%2C%20And%20What's%20Open%2C%20What's%20Closed%20In%20Delhi%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20traffic%20restrictions%20will%20come%20into%20effect%20from%20the%20night%20of%20September%207%20and%20remain%20in%20place%20September%2011.%20Here%20are%20some%20of%20the%20FAQs%20shared%20by%20the%20Delhi%20Traffic%20Police%20for%20the%20benefit%20of%20commuters%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20will%20the%20G20%20summit%20affect%20traffic%20movement%20in%20Delhi%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20the%20regulations%20will%20be%20enforced%20in%20the%20area%20where%20the%20summit%20will%20be%20held%20in%20the%20New%20Delhi%20district.%20Outside%20the%20New%20Delhi%20Municipal%20Council%20(NDMC)%20area%2C%20the%20flow%20of%20general%20traffic%20will%20remain%20unaffected%2C%20with%20the%20exception%20of%20National%20Highway%2048%20(NH-48).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMovement%20of%20passengers%20to%20airport%2C%20railway%20stations%20and%20interstate%20bus%20terminals%20(ISBTs)%20will%20be%20facilitated%20as%20all%20these%20facilities%20will%20be%20operational%20even%20during%20the%20G20%20summit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWill%20there%20be%20any%20restrictions%20on%20public%20transportation%20during%20the%20G20%20Summit%20in%20Delhi%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Delhi%20Traffic%20Police%2C%20there%20may%20be%20some%20limitations%20as%20certain%20modes%20of%20public%20transport%20and%20certain%20routes%20of%20public%20transportation%20will%20be%20modified%20or%20temporarily%20suspended%20during%20the%20G20%20summit.%20Airport%2C%20railway%2C%20metro%20services%2C%20interstate%20buses%20and%20city%20buses%2C%20and%20taxis%20will%20be%20functional%20but%20their%20movement%20will%20be%20affected.%20Metro%20services%20shall%20remain%20available%20at%20all%20the%20stations%20but%20boarding%20and%20de-boarding%20at%20Supreme%20Court%20will%20not%20be%20permitted%20from%205am%20on%20September%209%20to%2011pm%20on%20September%2010.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterstate%20buses%20will%20be%20allowed%20entry%20into%20Delhi%20but%20their%20termination%20points%20will%20be%20on%20the%20Ring%20Road%20based%20on%20the%20plan%20announced%20by%20the%20traffic%20police.%20City%20buses%20will%20operate%20on%20Ring%20Road%20and%20beyond%20towards%20Delhi%20borders%20and%20will%20be%20allowed%20to%20exit%20the%20national%20capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaxis%20will%20be%20allowed%20to%20enter%20New%20Delhi%20only%20if%20tourists%20can%20produce%20a%20valid%20hotel%20booking.%20Cabs%20carrying%20people%20living%20in%20the%20area%20and%20authorised%20vehicles%20will%20be%20allowed.%20So%20will%20be%20vehicles%20dealing%20with%20housekeeping%2C%20catering%2C%20waste%20management%20etc.%20for%20hotels%2C%20hospitals%20and%20other%20important%20installations.%20It%20is%20important%20to%20note%20that%20people%20living%20in%20New%20Delhi%20district%20will%20have%20to%20carry%20documents%20to%20prove%20their%20identity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20Traffic%20police%20has%20asked%20people%20to%20visit%20G20%20Traffic%20Virtual%20Help%20Desk%2C%20their%20website%20and%20social%20media%20handles%20for%20latest%20information%20and%20learn%20about%20changes%2C%20if%20any.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWill%20there%20be%20lockdown-like%20situation%20there%20in%20Delhi%20during%20the%20G20%20Summit%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20traffic%20police%20has%20assured%20there%20won't%20be%20any%20such%20situation%2C%20explaining%20that%20Metro%20and%20other%20public%20transport%20will%20be%20available%20during%20the%20summit%20duration%2C%20though%20with%20restrictions.%20It%20also%20said%20that%20all%20medical%20shops%2C%20grocery%20shops%2C%20milk%20booth%2C%20vegetable%2Ffruit%20shops%20will%20remain%20open%20throughout%20Delhi%2C%20including%20the%20New%20Delhi%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGeneral%20traffic%2C%20including%20all%20types%20of%20commercial%20vehicles%20and%20buses%20shall%20be%20allowed%20to%20ply%20on%20Ring%20Road%20and%20road%20network%20beyond%20Ring%20Road%20towards%20the%20borders%20of%20Delhi%2C%26quot%3B%20thr%20advisory%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWill%20parking%20be%20available%20near%20Pragati%20Maidan%20during%20the%20G20%20summit%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20Traffic%20Police%20has%20clarified%20that%20parking%20will%20be%20accessible%20only%20to%20authorised%20vehicles%2C%20since%20Pragati%20Maidan%20is%20the%20venue%20of%20the%20two-day%20summit.%20The%20traffic%20police%20has%20advised%20people%20to%20avoid%20use%20of%20private%20vehicles%20and%20explore%20alternative%20modes%20of%20transportation%2C%20such%20as%20Metro%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAre%20there%20any%20designated%20pick-up%20and%20drop-off%20points%20for%20private%20vehicles%20or%20taxis%20near%20Pragati%20Maidan%20during%20the%20G20%20Summit%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20advisory%20has%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20autorickshaws%20and%20taxis%20won't%20be%20allowed%20to%20enter%20the%20New%20Delhi%20district%20from%205am%20on%20September%2009%20to%2011.59pm%20on%20September%2010.%20However%2C%20these%20restrictions%20won't%20be%20applicable%20on%20taxis%20carrying%20tourists%20with%20valid%20hotel%20bookings%20and%20people%20who%20live%20in%20New%20Delhi%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWill%20there%20be%20any%20special%20arrangements%20for%20public%20transportation%20near%20Pragati%20Maidan%20during%20the%20G20%20Summit%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20Traffic%20Police%20has%20asked%20people%20to%20make%20maximum%20use%20of%20Metro%2C%20since%20it%20will%20be%20available%20for%20commuters%20near%20Pragati%20Maidan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20long%20are%20the%20anticipated%20traffic%20regulations%20expected%20to%20last%20during%20the%20G20%20Summit%20in%20Delhi%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Delhi%20Traffic%20Police%2C%20the%20restrictions%20will%20be%20in%20place%20from%20September%207-11%20but%20the%20duration%20can%20vary%20based%20on%20the%20summit's%20schedule%2C%20security%20requirements%20and%20other%20factors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EAre%20there%20any%20unique%20traffic%20control%20measures%20or%20technologies%20being%20implemented%20during%20the%20G20%20Summit%20in%20Delhi%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20Traffic%20Police%20will%20use%20advanced%20traffic%20control%20measures%20and%20technologies%20to%20manage%20the%20traffic.%20These%20can%20include%20smart%20traffic%20signals%2C%20real-time%20traffic%20updates%20through%20mobile%20apps%20and%20traffic%20surveillance%20systems%20to%20ensure%20smooth%20flow%20and%20minimise%20congestion.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693477440000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2F042ilhv8_delhi-g20-summit-photo-feature_625x300_22_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Fg20-summit-will-there-be-lockdown-like-situation-in-delhi-all-questions-answered-4345171%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20G20%20summit%20will%20be%20held%20on%20September%209%20and%2010%20at%20the%20newly-built%20Bharat%20Mandapam%20at%20Pragati%20Maidan.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Fg20-summit-will-there-be-lockdown-like-situation-in-delhi-all-questions-answered-4345171%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Fg20-summit-will-there-be-lockdown-like-situation-in-delhi-all-questions-answered-4345171%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Fg20-summit-will-there-be-lockdown-like-situation-in-delhi-all-questions-answered-4345171%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Jupiter%20Life%20Line%20Hospital%20IPO%20to%20open%20for%20public%20subscription%20on%20Sep%206%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693477430000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-04%2F26%2Ffull%2F1682532185-002.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fjupiter-life-line-hospital-ipo-to-open-for-public-subscription-on-sep-6-123083100604_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20initial%20share%20sale%20of%20multispecialty%20hospital%20chain%20Jupiter%20Life%