ion%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EBritish%20coffee%20shop%20chain%20Pret%20a%20Manger%20was%20fined%20%C2%A3800%2C000%20(just%20over%20%241%20million)%20after%20an%20employee%20was%20trapped%20in%20a%20freezer%20for%20more%20than%20two%20hours%20at%20one%20of%20its%20London%20stores%20and%20was%20later%20treated%20for%20suspected%20hypothermia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20employee%20at%20Pret's%20London%20Victoria%20Coach%20Station%20store%20was%20trapped%20in%20a%20walk-in%20commercial%20freezer%20typically%20set%20to%20around%200%20degrees%20Fahrenheit%2C%20Westminster%20City%20Council%20said%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.westminster.gov.uk%2Fnews%2Fpret-manger-fined-ps800000-after-cafe-worker-left-locked-walk-freezer%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epress%20release%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20worker%2C%20who%20was%20wearing%20just%20jeans%20and%20a%20t-shirt%2C%20tried%20to%20keep%20warm%20by%20moving%20around%20but%20her%20breathing%20gradually%20became%20restricted%20and%20she%20started%20to%20lose%20sensation%20in%20her%20thighs%20and%20feet%2C%20the%20Council%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTo%20try%20and%20keep%20warm%2C%20she%20tore%20up%20a%20cardboard%20box%20containing%20chocolate%20croissants%20to%20use%20as%20cover%20from%20the%20ventilator%20blowing%20out%20cold%20air%20but%20found%20that%20her%20hands%20were%20too%20cold%20and%20painful%20to%20break%20the%20box%20apart%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Council%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20spending%20around%20two%20and%20a%20half%20hours%20stuck%20in%20the%20freezer%2C%20the%20worker%20was%20eventually%20found%20by%20a%20colleague.%20She%20was%20%26quot%3Bin%20a%20state%20of%20distress%20and%20believing%20she%20was%20going%20to%20die%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Council%20said.%20The%20worker%20was%20then%20taken%20to%20hospital%20where%20she%20was%20treated%20for%20suspected%20hypothermia%2C%20the%20Council%20said.%20A%20spokesperson%20for%20Pret%20told%20Insider%20that%20the%20employee%20was%20discharged%20from%20hospital%20the%20same%20day.%20She%20has%20since%20returned%20to%20her%20job%20at%20Pret%2C%20working%20as%20a%20team%20leader.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20investigation%20by%20the%20Council's%20health%20and%20safety%20team%20found%20that%20Pret%20didn't%20have%20a%20suitable%20risk%20assessment%20for%20employees%20working%20in%20temperature-controlled%20environments.%20It%20also%20said%20that%20it%20found%20that%20Pret%20had%20received%20other%20callouts%20related%20to%20defective%20or%20frozen%20push%20buttons%20in%20the%20previous%2019%20months%2C%20including%20one%20at%20the%20same%20store%20in%20Victoria%20Coach%20Station%20in%20January%202020%20when%20a%20worker%20was%20trapped%20in%20the%20walk-in%20freezer%20after%20the%20internal%20door-release%20mechanism%20broke.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20Westminster%20Magistrates'%20Court%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20Pret%20pleaded%20guilty%20to%20a%20health%20and%20safety%20offense%20and%20was%20ordered%20to%20pay%20%C2%A3800%2C000%2C%20reduced%20by%20the%20district%20judge%20from%20an%20initial%20%C2%A31.6%20million%20(%242%20million)%20because%20the%20company%20had%20entered%20an%20early%20guilty%20plea%20and%20had%20advanced%20mitigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20incredibly%20sorry%20for%20our%20colleague's%20experience%20and%20understand%20how%20distressing%20this%20must%20have%20been%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Pret%20spokesperson%20told%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20carried%20out%20a%20full%20review%20and%20have%20worked%20with%20the%20manufacturer%20to%20develop%20a%20solution%20to%20stop%20this%20from%20happening%20again.%20Following%20the%20incident%2C%20we%20have%20revisited%20all%20our%20existing%20systems%20and%20where%20appropriate%2C%20enhanced%20these%20processes%2C%20and%20have%20cooperated%20fully%20with%20Westminster%20City%20Council's%20investigation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pret.com%2Fen-US%2Fpret-a-manger-usa-partners-with-dallas-holdings%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDecember%202022%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20coffee%20and%20sandwich%20chain%20had%20around%20550%20stores%2C%20with%20the%20vast%20majority%20in%20the%20UK%20%E2%80%93%20especially%20London%20%E2%80%93%20but%20also%20in%20other%20markets%20including%20the%20US%2C%20France%2C%20Dubai%2C%20and%20Hong%20Kong.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpret-a-manger-fines-1-million-worker-stuck-in-freezer-2023-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693476745000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64f05f0cf8c8620019612b4e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpret-a-manger-fines-1-million-worker-stuck-in-freezer-2023-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Pret%20worker%20tried%20to%20use%20a%20croissant%20box%20to%20cover%20a%20ventilator%20blowing%20out%20cold%20air%20but%20her%20hands%20were%20too%20cold%20and%20painful%20to%20tear%20the%20box%20apart.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22gdean%40insider.com%20(Grace%20Dean)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A9%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpret-a-manger-fines-1-million-worker-stuck-in-freezer-2023-8%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22When%20Dharmendra%20abused%20a%20house%20help%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693476726000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-103245584%2Cimgsize-27522.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fsunny-deol-recalls-an-incident-when-dharmendra-abused-a-house-help-and-his-dadi-made-the-house-help-abuse-him-back%2Farticleshow%2F103245604.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F103245604.cms%5C%22%20hspa