t%20taking%20it%20slow.%20We're%20not%20stopping%20to%20say%20hello%20to%20anyone.%20But%20that%20being%20said%2C%20once%20summer%20comes%20around%2C%20it's%20just%20magical%20here.%20Everyone%20is%20smiling%20and%20happy%20and%20outside%20drinking%20beer.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20the%20same%20with%20the%20Norwegian%20people.%20As%20soon%20as%20you%20warm%20them%20up%20a%20little%20bit%20and%20I%20show%20them%20that%20I%20can%20speak%20a%20little%20Norwegian%20or%20tell%20them%20I've%20lived%20here%20for%20nine%20years%2C%20I%20think%20I%20kind%20of%20gain%20some%20respect.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20winters%20are%20not%20for%20the%20faint%20of%20heart%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20winters%20for%20me%20are%20not%20it.%20There%20are%20some%20cities%20in%20Norway%20where%20the%20sun%20doesn't%20show%20at%20all%20and%20they%20have%20mirrors%20on%20the%20mountain%20to%20reflect%20what%20little%20sunlight%20there%20is.%20Some%20of%20my%20friends%20have%20sun%20lamps%20they%20wake%20up%20to%20every%20day.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22696%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Emily%20Northway%20skiing%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64ef80620ce10a00183bc84b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22522%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ENorthway%20said%20picking%20up%20cold%20weather%20sports%20is%20one%20way%20to%20fight%20the%20winter%20blues.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Emily%20Northway%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20gone%20on%20trips%20to%20Cape%20Town%20the%20past%20two%20years%2C%20so%20that's%20my%20life%20hack.%20You%20also%20make%20plans%20with%20friends%20to%20stay%20social%20because%20it's%20so%20easy%20to%20go%20home%20and%20hibernate%20and%20just%20go%20to%20bed.%20But%20if%20you%20plan%20to%20meet%20for%20a%20glass%20of%20wine%20after%20work%2C%20or%20go%20for%20a%20walk%2C%20hike%2C%20cross-country%20ski%2C%20or