g%20from%20home%20and%20was%20found%20dead%20at%20her%20residence%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20younger%20sister%20allegedly%20left%20the%20house%20with%20a%20man%20the%20same%20day%2C%20as%20per%20CCTV%20footage%2C%20police%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGold%20ornaments%20and%20Rs%202%20lakh%20cash%20were%20also%20missing%20from%20the%20house%2C%20as%20per%20the%20complaint%20by%20the%20techie's%20parents%2C%20police%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20parents%20of%20the%20sisters%2C%20who%20were%20in%20Hyderabad%20to%20attend%20some%20event%2C%20had%20spoken%20to%20them%20over%20phone%20on%20Monday%20but%20after%20not%20getting%20any%20response%20from%20them%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20asked%20the%20neighbours%20to%20check%2C%20the%20police%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20neighbours%20noticed%20the%20techie's%20body%20on%20a%20sofa%20in%20a%20room%20and%20alerted%20the%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20liquor%20bottles%20were%20found%20in%20the%20house%20and%20it%20was%20suspected%20that%20there%20were%20scuffle%20marks%20on%20the%20body%20of%20the%20woman%2C%20police%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%20arrests%20have%20been%20made%20so%20far%20in%20the%20case%20of%20the%20suspicious%20death%20of%20the%20woman%20techie%2C%20a%20senior%20police%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20parents%20of%20the%20techie%20were%20away%20from%20the%20town%20on%20that%20day%2C%20Superintendent%20of%20Police%20Eggadi%20Bhaskar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20cause%20of%20death%20of%20the%20techie%20would%20be%20known%20after%20the%20forensic%20report%20is%20received%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20information%2C%20the%20two%20(the%20techie's%20younger%20sister%20and%20the%20man)%20are%20moving%20in%20Hyderabad%20and%20efforts%20are%20on%20to%20catch%20them%2C%20police%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOnce%20we%20get%20them%2C%20we%20can%20assess%20the%20cause%20of%20death%20of%20the%20woman%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Superintendent%20of%20Police%20added.%