lar%20Jol%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E(Bengal%E2%80%99s%20soil%2C%20Bengal%E2%80%99s%20water)%2C%20which%20he%20penned%20protesting%20the%20colonial%20bifurcation%20of%20Bengal%20in%201905%2C%20may%20be%20adopted%20as%20the%20%E2%80%98state%20anthem%E2%80%99%20with%20changed%20lyrics.%20The%20usage%20of%20%E2%80%98Bengali%E2%80%99%20in%20the%20song%20can%20be%20replaced%20with%20%E2%80%98Bengal%E2%80%99%2C%20she%20suggested.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20two%20stanzas%20of%20the%20four-stanza%20song%20seek%20blessings%20and%20satiety%20for%20Bengal%E2%80%99s%20soil%2C%20water%2C%20air%2C%20fruits%2C%20homes%2C%20markets%2C%20fields%20and%20forests.%20The%20next%20two%20stanzas%20seek%20fulfilment%20of%20the%20resolve%2C%20hope%2C%20action%20and%20language%20of%20Bengalis%20and%2C%20unity%20of%20the%20Bengalis%E2%80%99%20souls%20and%20minds%20and%20of%20all%20the%20brothers%20and%20sisters%20in%20Bengali%20households.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Tuesday%20meeting%20was%20held%20in%20the%20conference%20room%20of%20the%20state%20secretariat%2C%20Nabanna%2C%20to%20discuss%20choosing%20a%20day%20to%20be%20celebrated%20as%C2%A0%3Cem%3EPoschimbanga%20Dibos%2C%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3Eor%20West%20Bengal%20Day.%20Apart%20from%20political%20parties%2C%20the%20government%20had%20invited%20members%20of%20civil%20society%2C%20religious%20groups%2C%20industry%20and%20major%20sporting%20clubs.%20The%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%2C%20Left%20Front%20parties%20and%20the%20Congress%20did%20not%20send%20any%20representatives%2C%20but%20leaders%20of%20leftist%20parties%20Socialist%20Unity%20Centre%20of%20India%20(Communist)%20or%20SUCI(C)%20and%20CPI(ML)(Liberation)%20attended%20the%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESUCI(C)%E2%80%99s%20Amitava%20Chatterjee%2C%20a%20central%20committee%20member%20of%20the%20party%2C%20promptly%20objected%20to%20the%20chief%20minister%E2%80%99s%20proposal%2C%20saying%20that%20tinkering%20with%20Tagore%E2%80%99s%20lyrics%20would%20cause%20an%20unnecessary%20controversy%20and%20should%20not%20be%20attempted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20chief%20minister%20seemed%20to%20agree%20and%20asked%20if%20Dwijendralal%20Ray%E2%80%99s%C2%A0%3Cem%3EDhano%20Dhanyo%20Pushpo%20Bhora%3C%2Fem%3E%20could%20be%20considered.%20Not%20many%20agreed%2C%20possibly%20because%20the%20song%20is%20an%20ode%20to%20the%20country%20%E2%80%93%20as%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20greatest%20of%20all%20countries%E2%80%9D.%20No%20decision%20was%20arrived%20at%20during%20the%20meeting%20and%20Banerjee%20said%20it%20would%20be%20further%20discussed%20in%20the%20assembly%20on%20September%207.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20Banerjee%20was%20quick%20to%20bury%20the%20topic%20of%20changing%20the%20Tagore%20song%E2%80%99s%20lyrics%2C%20the%20very%20reason%20the%20idea%20of%20replacing%20%E2%80%98Bengali%E2%80%99%20in%20the%20song%20with%20%E2%80%98Bengal%E2%80%99%20came%20to%20her%20in%20the%20first%20place%20is%20her%20dilemma%20over%20adopting%20a%20Bengali%20identity-based%20politics%20to%20counter%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Hindu%20nationalism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20has%20been%20plaguing%20her%20since%202017%20when%20the%20Sangh%20%3Cem%3Eparivar%3C%2Fem%3E%20%E2%80%93%20the%20group%20of%20organisations%20belonging%20to%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20ideological-organisation%20parent%2C%20the%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%20(RSS)%20%E2%80%93%20first%20made%20its%20presence%20felt%20in%20the%20state%20by%20organising%20massive%20Ram%20Navami%20processions%20in%20every%20district.%20She%20had%20asked%20why%20the%20BJP%20was%20imposing%20an%20alien%20festival%20on%20the%20day%20of%20Bengal%E2%80%99s%20own%20Annapurna%20Puja.%20She%20adopted%20the%20Joy%20Bangla%20(Victory%20to%20Bengal)%20of%20Bangladesh%20Liberation%20War%20fame%20as%20one%20of%20her%20party%E2%80%99s%20slogans%20soon%20after.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20she%20had%20toned%20down%20on%20her%20Bengali%20identity%20pitch%20by%20the%20end%20of%202019%2C%20reportedly%20on%20the%20advice%20of%20political%20strategist%20Prashant%20Kishor%2C%20who%20is%20understood%20to%20have%20told%20the%20party%20that%20excluding%20the%20Hindi-speaking%20population%20from%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20outreach%20initiatives%20would%20be%20wrong.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYet%2C%20the%202021%20assembly%20election%20saw%20the%20party%20riding%20on%20anti-outsider%20sentiments%20with%20slogans%20like%C2%A0%3Cem%3EBangla%20Nijer%20Meyeke%20Chay%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0(Bengal%20wants%20her%20own%20daughter).%20The%20famous%C2%A0%3Cem%3EKhela%20Hobe%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0song%20had%20wordings%20like%C2%A0%3Cem%3EBaire%20Theke%20Borgi%20Asey%2F%20Niyom%20Korey%20Proti%20Masey%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E(The%20Borgi%20outsiders%20keep%20paying%20their%20monthly%20visits)%2C%20which%20eventually%20found%20its%20place%20in%20wall%20graffiti%20across%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20word%20Borgi%20originally%20referred%20to%20the%20Maratha%20raiders%20of%20the%2018th%20century%20who%20earned%20notoriety%20in%20Bengal%2C%20the%20term%20in%20recent%20years%20was%20also%20tacitly%20used%20to%20refer%20to%20Kailash%20Vijayvargiya%20(pronounced%20Bijoyborgiyo%20in%20Bengali)%2C%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20then%20Bengal%20in-charge%20who%20is%20from%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%20%E2%80%9CBengal%20won%E2%80%99t%20bow%20before%20outsiders%2C%E2%80%9D%20Banerjee%20thundered%20in%20rally%20after%20rally.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20the%20government%20and%20the%20party%20have%20also%20tried%20to%20address%20the%20interests%20of%20the%20Hindi-speaking%20population%2C%20from%20the%20government%20announcing%20a%20Hindi%20university%20to%20the%20party%20opening%20a%20Hindi%20cell.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CShe%20has%20frequently%20been%20tempted%20by%20the%20prospect%20of%20countering%20Hindu%20nationalism%20with%20Bengali%20ethnic%20politics%20but%20has%20also%20been%20dissuaded%20by%20the%20prospect%20of%20alienating%20speakers%20of%20other%20languages%2C%20who%20make%20up%20nearly%2014%25%20of%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20population%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20a%20TMC%20Lok%20Sabha%20MP%2C%20who%20did%20not%20want%20to%20be%20named%20in%20a%20comment%20involving%20the%20party%20chief.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20leader%20had%20a%20different%20opinion%3A%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20not%20really%20the%20Hindi-speaking%20people%20of%20south%20Bengal%20that%20deter%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20from%20adopting%20a%20DMK-like%20ethnic%20political%20line%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20the%20Nepali-speaking%20people%20of%20Darjeeling.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20making%20of%20a%20map%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20recent%20developments%20over%20choosing%20a%C2%A0%3Cem%3EPoschimbango%20Dibos%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20a%20state%20song%20arose%20after%20West%20Bengal%20governor%20C.V.%20Ananda%20Bose%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Findia%2Fstory%2Fbengal-foundation-day-june-20-mamata-banerjee-writes-governor-cv-ananda-bose-2395110-2023-06-19%5C%22%3Edecided%20to%20celebrate%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0June%2020%20as%20state%20foundation%20day.%20This%20was%20the%20day%2C%20in%201947%2C%20when%20the%20undivided%20Bengal%20assembly%20decided%20that%20the%20state%20would%20be%20bifurcated%20when%20India%20partitions%20and%20the%20eastern%20part%20would%20go%20to%20Pakistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Bengal%20unit%20had%20long%20been%20celebrating%20June%2020%20as%20the%20%E2%80%98foundation%20day%E2%80%99%20of%20West%20Bengal%2C%20which%20they%20claim%20was%20conceived%20as%20a%20%E2%80%98homeland%20for%20Bengali%20Hindus%E2%80%99.%20Triggering%20the%20bitter%20memories%20of%20the%20Partition%20and%20pre-Partition%20riots%20has%20topped%20the%20Sangh%20parivar%E2%80%99s%20agenda%20in%20West%20Bengal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20precisely%20to%20keep%20this%20memory%20alive%20that%20the%20Union%20home%20ministry%20had%20not%20consented%20to%20the%20state%20government%E2%80%99s%20proposal%20for%20renaming%20West%20Bengal%20as%20Bangla%2C%20Bongo%20or%20Bongodesh.%20Senior%20BJP%20leaders%20have%20repeatedly%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Findia-news-india%2Fbjp-on-renaming-west-bengal-will-urge-center-not-to-approve-mamatas-plan-2956838%2F%5C%22%3Ealleged%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20attempt%20to%20remove%20the%20%E2%80%98West%E2%80%99%20from%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20name%20was%20part%20of%20the%20TMC%E2%80%99s%20conspiracy%20to%20%E2%80%98erase%20the%20memories%20of%20Partition%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMamata%20Banerjee%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FANI%2Fstatus%2F1670814072651251712%5C%22%3Eobjected%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0to%20the%20governor%E2%80%99s%20choice%20of%20the%20date%2C%20saying%20it%20rekindled%20unpleasant%20memories%2C%20and%20subsequently%20proposed%C2%A0%3Cem%3EPoila%20Boishakh%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20first%20day%20of%20the%20Bengali%20calendar%2C%20usually%20on%20April%2014%2F15.%20The%20government%20is%20taking%20public%20opinion%20and%20asked%20people%20interested%20to%20send%20their%20suggestions%20to%20former%20bureaucrat%20Alapan%20Bandyopadhyay%2C%20currently%20the%20chief%20advisor%20to%20the%20chief%20minister%2C%20by%20September%205.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBangla%20Pokkho%2C%20a%20Bengali%20ethnic%20rights%20group%2C%20has%20objected%20to%20both%20proposed%20dates.%20They%20argue%20that%20the%20map%20of%20West%20Bengal%20decided%20on%20June%2020%20did%20not%20include%20Purulia%20district%2C%20which%20was%20then%20part%20of%20Bihar.%20%E2%80%9CWest%20Bengal%20got%20its%20present%20shape%20and%20map%20on%20November%201%2C%201956%2C%20with%20the%20inclusion%20of%20Purulia.%20That%20should%20be%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20foundation%20day%2C%E2%80%9D%20Garga%20Chatterjee%2C%20the%20general%20secretary%20of%20the%20organisation%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChatterjee%20also%20alleged%20that%20by%20proposing%20change%20in%20the%20lyrics%20of%20the%20Tagore%20song%2C%20the%20chief%20minister%20was%20indulging%20in%20%E2%80%98appeasement%20politics%E2%80%99.%20He%20did%20not%20clarify%20who%20Banerjee%20was%20appeasing.%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20clear%20she%20was%20not%20appeasing%20the%20Bengalis%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%2C%20indeed%2C%20are%20several%20differences%20in%20how%20West%20Bengal%E2%80%99s%20map%20was%20perceived%20on%20June%2020%2C%201947%2C%20and%20how%20it%20actually%20came%20to%20be.%20The%20June%2020%20decision%20meant%20Hindu-majority%20districts%20of%20Bengal%20would%20stay%20with%20India%20but%20West%20Bengal%E2%80%99s%20new%20map%20was%20still%20not%20clear%2C%20especially%20over%20the%20fate%20of%20districts%20like%20Khulna%2C%20Nadia%2C%20Dinajpur%2C%20Malda%2C%20Murshidabad%20and%20Jessore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20August%201947%2C%20Nadia%20district%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmailtrack.io%2Ftrace%2Flink%2F6798f67630e69bedbe878840c761a15b893a2c17%3Furl%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fcensusindia.gov.in%252Fnada%252Findex.php%252Fcatalog%252F30075%252Fdownload%252F33256%252F44366_1951_NAD.pdf%26userId%3D7302199%26signature%3D75e95f3a2e0c9614%5C%22%3Ewas%20bifurcated%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20with%20its%20Muslim-majority%20areas%2C%20Kushtia%2C%20Chuadanga%20and%20Meherpur%2C%20going%20to%20East%20Pakistan.%20The%20Bongan%20sub-division%20of%20Jessore%20district%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmailtrack.io%2Ftrace%2Flink%2F20c7a3579045c415ef6be7e4a72fcc1e5c1f7406%3Furl%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fnorth24parganas.gov.in%252Fabout_district%252Fhistory%26userId%3D7302199%26signature%3D66e47ea2a50ce21f%5C%22%3Ecame%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0to%20West%20Bengal.%20Malda%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmailtrack.io%2Ftrace%2Flink%2Fe835c0a526ffc022ad1642eb2ac4668b61b14cc2%3Furl%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fmalda.gov.in%252Fhistory%252F%26userId%3D7302199%26signature%3D57f87e022d900dc6%5C%22%3Ewas%20part%20of%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0either%20the%20Bhagalpur%20division%20of%20Bihar%20or%20Rajshahi%20division%20of%20Eastern%20Bengal%20and%20Radcliffe%E2%80%99s%20boundary%20commission%20report%20