.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Udhampur-Srinagar-Baramulla%20rail%20line%20project%20has%20a%20cost%20overrun%20of%20Rs%2037%2C012%20crore.%20It%20was%20sanctioned%20in%201995%20at%20an%20original%20estimated%20budget%20of%20Rs%202%2C500%20crore.%20The%20project%20is%20delayed%20by%20more%20than%2021%20years%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Lalitpur-Satna-Rewa%20Singruli%20project%E2%80%99s%20escalated%20budget%20has%20touched%20Rs%208%2C249%20crore.%20It%20was%20sanctioned%20in%201998%20with%20an%20original%20estimated%20cost%20of%20Rs%20248%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20BG%20rail%20line%20from%20Byrnihat%20to%20Shilong%2C%20sanctioned%20in%202010%20with%20an%20original%20budget%20of%20Rs%20906%20crore%2C%20is%20delayed%20with%20the%20escalated%20budget%20reaching%20Rs%208%2C324%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20railway%E2%80%99s%20eastern%20dedicated%20freight%20corridor%20project%2C%20sanctioned%20in%202006%20with%20an%20estimated%20budget%20of%20Rs%2011%2C589%20crore%2C%20is%20running%20behind%20its%20original%20schedule%20with%20the%20budget%20escalating%20to%20Rs%2051%2C219%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20of%20this%20information%20is%20available%20in%20the%20July%202023%20report%20shared%20with%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBesides%20railways%2C%20the%20419%20road%20transport%20and%20highways%20projects%20are%20delayed%20from%20their%20original%20scheduled%20deadlines%2C%20inflating%20the%20budget%20heavily.%20The%20total%20original%20cost%20of%201%2C646%20projects%2C%20including%20that%20of%20railways%2C%20was%20Rs%2023%2C92%2C837.89%20crore%20and%20their%20anticipated%20completion%20cost%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20Rs%2028%2C58%2C394.39%20crore%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20newspaper%20reported%2C%20citing%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693471238000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F10%2F16111107%2F5264934981_08748b0f32_k.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in