is-facil.ghtml%5C%22%3Esaid%20the%20%3Cem%3EG1%3C%2Fem%3E%20report%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20woman%20is%20in%20a%20relationship%20with%20another%20man%2C%20who%20has%20not%20yet%20been%20identified.%20She%20claimed%20she%20met%20the%20man%20on%20a%20dating%20app%20and%20invited%20him%20to%20her%20home%20around%20the%20same%20time%20when%20Silva%20was%20killed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFloriano%20initially%20told%20the%20police%20that%20she%20and%20the%20man%20took%20drugs%20and%20slept%20together%20-%20and%20that%20Silva%20was%20already%20dead%20when%20she%20woke%20up.%20At%20that%20time%2C%20she%20denied%20killing%20her%20daughter%20but%20did%20admit%20to%20placing%20the%20body%20parts%20in%20fridge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20were%20discovered%20by%20her%20boyfriend's%20mother.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%2C%20during%20questioning%20at%20the%20police%20station%2C%20Floriano%20confessed%20to%20taking%20drugs%20and%20killing%20the%20girl.%20The%20woman%20further%20said%20that%20she%20stabbed%20the%20child%20was%20she%20was%20brushing%20her%20teeth%2C%20as%20per%20%3Cem%3EG1%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFloriano%20said%20she%20placed%20the%20body%20parts%20in%20a%20refrigerator%20and%20disposed%20it%20of%20in%20a%20nearby%20sewer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20authorities%20said%20that%20Floriano%20had%20stabbed%20Silva%20in%20the%20chest%20and%20confessed%20to%20cooking%20some%20of%20the%20remains%20to%20destroy%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESilva's%20birthday%20was%20on%20August%206%2C%20and%20the%20police%20are%20now%20investigating%20if%20she%20died%20before%20or%20after%20this%20date.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693469820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fbvrdl0t_brazil-police-car-generic-1200_625x300_31_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fbrazil-woman-arrested-for-killing-daughter-and-chopping-her-body-searched-internet-for-easier-way-police-4344689%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%2