.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fpakistan%2Foverseas-pakistanis-urge-president-alvi-to-punish-those-involved-in-jaranwala-incident%2Famp_articleshow%2F103229836.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fpakistan%2Foverseas-pakistanis-urge-president-alvi-to-punish-those-involved-in-jaranwala-incident%2Famp_articleshow%2F103229836.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Anonymous%20buyer%20of%20world's%20largest%20whisky%20bottle%20revealed%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693451760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F08%2F768x432%2Fskynews-whisky-vietnam_6268645.jpg%3F20230831043404%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fanonymous-buyer-of-worlds-largest-whisky-bottle-revealed-12951175%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20anonymous%20buyer%20of%20the%20world's%20largest%20bottle%20of%20whisky%20has%20been%20revealed%20as%20a%20world-record%20breaking%20spirits%20aficionado%20in%20Vietnam.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A205%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fanonymous-buyer-of-worlds-largest-whisky-bottle-revealed-12951175%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fanonymous-buyer-of-worlds-largest-whisky-bottle-revealed-12951175%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fanonymous-buyer-of-worlds-largest-whisky-bottle-revealed-12951175%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Is%20Indian%20Agriculture%20Following%20Two%20Policies%20%E2%80%93%20One%20at%20WTO%20and%20Another%20at%20Home%3F%26nbsp%3B%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F31083338%2FScreenshot-2023-08-31-at-8.30.26.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3ERecent%20statements%20in%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack.com%2Fredirect%2F736c84c2-d4da-42a4-87c0-b7d164d46f4d%3Fj%3DeyJ1IjoiYWt5Mm8ifQ.6MWfvlP9rau_ovHEjX2OsfccTssIZEXNjPP_vKEvs5I%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fsubstack.com%2Fredirect%2F736c84c2-d4da-42a4-87c0-b7d164d46f4d%3Fj%253DeyJ1IjoiYWt5Mm8ifQ.6MWfvlP9rau_ovHEjX2OsfccTssIZEXNjPP_vKEvs5I%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1693535732303000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw0QLVOsPfhv3UNWKKO_BjEj%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emedia%3C%2Fa%3E%20put%20the%20Modi%20government%E2%80%99s%20position%20at%20the%20World%20Trade%20Organisation%20on%20Minimum%20Support%20Price%20(MSP)%20and%20the%20public%20storage%20of%20food%20grains%20on%20shaky%20ground.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20primary%20trigger%20for%20the%20confusion%20was%20the%20June%207%20cabinet%20meeting%20which%20announced%20an%20MSP%20hikes%20in%20the%20range%20of%206-10%25%20for%20a%20variety%20of%20crops.%20This%20step%20quickly%20drew%20the%20ire%20of%20Niti%20Aayog%20and%20the%20commerce%20ministry.%20So%20the%20real%20question%20is%2C%20what%20is%20happening%20to%20agrarian%20policy%2C%20globally%20and%20domestically%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20the%20agriculture%20ministry%20supported%20the%20move%20go%20grant%20farmers%20inflation-adjusted%20remunerations%2C%20Niti%20Aayog%20anticipated%20inflationary%20pressures%20on%20the%20economy%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20increase%20suggested%20in%20MSP%20varies%20from%205.3%25%20in%20the%20case%20of%20urad%20to%20more%20than%2010%25%20in%20crops%20like%20cotton%20(long%20staple)%2C%20sesame%20and%20moong.%20If%20this%20much%20increase%20is%20given%20to%20MSP%2C%20it%20will%20be%20very%20difficult%20to%20keep%20food%20inflation%20in%20the%20stipulated%20range%20of%204-6%25%2C%20which%20is%20very%20important%20for%20macro-economic%20stability.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%20don%E2%80%99t%20forget%20that%20as%20CEO%20Niti%20Aayog%2C%20Amitabh%20Kant%20had%20advocated%20for%20abolishing%20MSP.%20Strike%20one%20MSP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20more%20shocking%20was%20the%20commerce%20ministry%E2%80%99s%20response%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20per%20WTO%E2%80%99s%20Agreement%20on%20Agriculture%20(AoA)%20related%20to%20public%20stockholding%20for%20food%20security%20purposes%2C%20the%20Market%20Price%20support%20(MPS)%20provided%20through%20procurement%20of%20crops%20by%20the%20government%20at%20administered%20price%20(MSP%20in%20India)%20is%20required%20to%20be%20notified%20to%20the%20WTO.%20Further%2C%20it%20needs%20to%20be%20ensured%20that%20product-specific%20support%20is%20within%20the%20%3Cem%3Ede%20minimis%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0limit%2C%20that%20is%2C%2010%25%20of%20the%20value%20of%20the%20production%20of%20the%20respective%20crop.%20Similar%C2%A0%3Cem%3Ede%20minimis%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0limit%20also%20applies%20to%20non-product%20specific%20price%20support%20across%20the%20agriculture%20sector.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20also%20been%20challenged%20by%20the%20developed%20countries%20for%20giving%20subsidies%20over%2010%25%2C%20exceeding%20the%C2%A0%3Cem%3Ede%20minimis%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0limit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20also%20did%20say%20reportedly%20that%20MSP%20production%20should%20not%20be%20open-ended%20and%20predetermined%20targets%20should%20be%20specified%20simultaneously%20for%20procurement%20of%20MSP%20crops.%20To%20understand%20their%20state%20we%20need%20to%20go%20back%20to%20the%20WTO.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%2C%20too%2C%20there%20is%20a%20deep%20confusion%20about%20which%20way%20is%20India%20headed%2C%20because%20ever%20since%20the%20WTO%20was%20born%20out%20of%20General%20Agreement%20on%20Tariffs%20and%20Trade%20(GATT)%2C%20India%20has%20been%20a%20major%20voice%20advocating%20for%20global%20south-centric%20policies%20of%20agriculture%20and%20farmers%E2%80%99%20welfare.%20Our%20positions%20on%20price%20support%2C%20the%20public%20food%20distribution%20systems%20and%20subsidies%20for%20farmers%20have%20often%20been%20challenged%20by%20the%20US%20and%20other%20developed%20countries%20as%20being%20too%20protectionist%20and%20barring%20free%20trade.%20But%20we%20did%20manage%20to%20survive%20until%20the%20WTO%E2%80%99s%2012th%20ministerial%20conference%20(MC12)%20concluded%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20India%20reportedly%20withheld%20support%20from%20Food%20Security%20and%20the%20World%20Food%20Programme%20discussion%2C%20which%20was%20pressing%20for%20government-to-government%20food%20grain%20purchases%20to%20be%20approved%20from%20PSH%20(public%20stockholding%20programmes%20for%20food%20security%20purposes%20like%20the%20public%20distribution%20system%20programme)%20and%20then%20under%20pressure%20from%20the%20US%2C%20Brazil%2C%20Uruguay%2C%20Australia%2C%20and%20Thailand%20scuttled%20and%20agreed%20to%20the%20WFP%20proposition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20basically%20allows%20for%20WFP%20to%20procure%20food%20grains%20from%20countries%20like%20India%2C%20despite%20India%20putting%20up%20trade%20or%20export%20restrictions.%20Whoever%20controls%20the%20WFP%20now%20has%20the%20power%20to%20circumvent%20any%20government%20policies%20and%20get%20grain%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20strike%20came%20when%20India%20led%20a%20resolute%20endeavour%20to%20establish%20a%20lasting%20resolution%20for%20public%20stockholding%20programs%20aimed%20at%20ensuring%20food%20security%20at%20the%20WTO.%20Over%2080%20nations%20united%20in%20support%20of%20this%20cause%2C%20with%20India%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20the%20campaign.%20However%2C%20formidable%20opposition%20from%20the%20US%2C%20EU%2C%20Australia%2C%20and%20various%20South%20American%20nations%20created%20significant%20obstacles.%20Regrettably%2C%20despite%20tenacious%20efforts%2C%20the%20discussions%20surrounding%20this%20critical%20issue%20were%20ultimately%20dismantled%2C%20leaving%20no%20indication%20of%20their%20outcome.%20Remarkably%2C%20this%20marks%20an%20unprecedented%20occurrence%20in%20the%20annals%20of%20WTO%20negotiations%2C%20as%20the%20realm%20of%20agriculture%20is%20now%20devoid%20of%20any%20decision%20or%20declaration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20what%20does%20all%20this%20mean%3F%20Simply%20put%2C%20the%20government%20is%20saying%20one%20thing%20at%20the%20WTO%20and%20another%20thing%20to%20its%20farmers%20as%20the%20election%20year%20approaches%2C%20and%20is%20increasing%20MSP%20following%20only%20electoral%20logic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20agriculture%20ministry%20is%20right%20%E2%80%95%20inflation%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20been%20adjusted%20since%201986%20and%20a%20sudden%20spike%20in%20fuel%20and%20fertiliser%20costs%2C%20plus%20wheat%20price%20volatility%2C%20have%20pushed%20inflation%20far%20beyond%20the%20average.%20The%20devaluation%20of%20the%20rupee%20and%20the%20rising%20dollar%20has%20also%20added%20to%20India%E2%80%99s%20problems.%20It%20is%20about%20time%20that%20India%20takes%20up%20the%20WTO%20challenge%20and%20once%20again%20steps%20forward%20as%20a%20leader%20of%20the%20global%20south%20in%20agricultural%20negotiations%2C%20and%20also%20negotiates%20a%20policy%20that%20ensures%20food%20security%20and%20protects%20the%20interests%20of%20farmers%20at%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIndra%20Shekhar%20Singh%C2%A0is%20former%20director%2C%20policy%20and%20outreach%2C%20the%20National%20Seed%20Association%20of%20India.%20He%20tweets%20at%C2%A0%40Indrassingh.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693451180000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F31083338%2FScreenshot-2023-08-31-at-8.30.26.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fagriculture%2Fmodi-agriculture-wto-msp-policies-niti-aayog%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Simply%20put%2C%20the%20government%20is%20saying%20one%20thing%20at%20the%20WTO%20and%20another%20thing%20to%20its%20farmers%20as%20the%20election%20year%20approaches%2C%20and%20is%20increasing%20MSP%20following%20only%20electoral%20logic.%C2%A0%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fagriculture%2Fmod