3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20the%20estate%20came%20to%20be%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESituated%20right%20in%20the%20lap%20of%20the%20glorious%20Western%20Ghats%2C%20Shreedev%20shares%20that%20the%20main%20draw%20at%20Woodway%20is%20the%20heritage%20and%20history%20associated%20with%20it.%20Built%20in%20the%20classic%20Gothic%20architectural%20style%2C%20one%20feels%20the%20magic%20right%20upon%20entering%20through%20its%20doors.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CA%20British%20gentleman%20owned%20the%20property%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Shreedev.%20%E2%80%9CWhile%20he%20had%20initially%20constructed%20a%20bungalow%20on%20the%20highest%20point%20of%20the%20land%2C%20and%20planned%20on%20living%20in%20it%2C%20the%20lack%20of%20water%20forced%20him%20to%20move%20lower%20down%20on%20the%20land%20and%20build%20a%20smaller%20house.%20Today%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F324508%2Fbest-pet-friendly-homestays-across-india-travel-vacation%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethat%20bungalow%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20Woodway%20Estate%2C%20where%20the%20gentleman%20would%20entertain%20guests%2C%20host%20officers%2C%20among%20others.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20story%20goes%20that%20after%20India%E2%80%99s%20independence%20from%20British%20Rule%20in%201947%2C%20the%20estate%20was%20sold%20to%20an%20Indian%20from%20whom%20Shreedev%E2%80%99s%20father%20later%20purchased%20it%20in%201975.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ETurning%20heritage%20into%20a%20home%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201125px)%20100vw%2C%201125px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FIMG_1073_11zon-1692369336.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221125%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Woodway%20Heritage%20Home%20is%20situated%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20the%20glorious%20Western%20Ghats%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FIMG_1073_11zon-1692369336.jpg%201125w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FIMG_1073_11zon-1692369336-300x186.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FIMG_1073_11zon-1692369336-500x310.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FIMG_1073_11zon-1692369336-768x477.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FIMG_1073_11zon-1692369336-150x93.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-327709%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22698%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EWoodway%20Heritage%20Home%20is%20situated%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20the%20glorious%20Western%20Ghats%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Susmitha%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShreedev%20was%20working%20in%20Bengaluru%20in%202000%20when%20he%20met%20Susmitha%2C%20an%20MBA%20graduate.%20The%20two%20fell%20in%20love%2C%20got%20married%2C%20and%20moved%20back%20to%20Chikmagalur%2C%20in%20a%20home%207%20km%20from%20the%20Woodway%20estate.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ravages%20of%20time%20were%20evident%20on%20Woodway.%20It%20had%20been%20locked%20for%20a%20year-and-a-half%20and%20the%20unpredictable%20climate%20of%20the%20state%20had%20taken%20its%20toll%20on%20the%20home.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20starting%20to%20crumble.%20The%20Mangalore%20tiles%20and%20mud%20walls%20were%20starting%20to%20chip%20away.%20When%20we%20saw%20it%20after%20all%20these%20years%2C%20we%20could%20tell%20it%20had%20seen%20much%20damage%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Susmitha.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20tough%20call%20awaited%20the%20couple.%20Should%20they%20restore%20the%20home%2C%20furnish%20it%20or%20leave%20it%20as%20is%3F%20But%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F284474%2Fhow-couple-quit-city-life-to-build-sustainable-homestay-in-uttarakhand%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esentimental%20value%20of%20the%20home%20%3C%2Fa%3Ecompelled%20them%20to%20choose%20the%20first%20option.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAnd%20we%E2%80%99re%20so%20glad%20we%20did%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20simple%20idea%20taking%20roots%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20couple%20decided%20to%20restore%20the%20place%2C%20they%20hadn%E2%80%99t%20thought%20of%20converting%20it%20into%20a%20homestay.%20The%20inspiration%20came%20after%20Susmitha%20read%20an%20article%20in%202000%20about%20the%20emergence%20of%20%E2%80%98homestay%20culture%E2%80%99%20in%20Coorg.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThen%20why%20not%20Chikmagalur%3F%E2%80%9D%20she%20thought.%20The%20city%20boasted%20of%20forests%2C%20waterfalls%2C%20and%20beautiful%20grasslands%2C%20all%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20the%20luscious%20Western%20Ghats.%20The%20couple%20wanted%20the%20city%20to%20be%20known%20on%20the%20world-map.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201600px)%20100vw%2C%201600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FPHOTO-2023-04-05-14-18-25_11zon-1692369085.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20heritage%20home%20offers%20bird%20watching%2C%20trekking%2C%20hiking%2C%20cycling%20and%20more%20to%20all%20adventure%20lovers%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FPHOTO-2023-04-05-14-18-25_11zon-1692369085.jpg%201600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FPHOTO-2023-04-05-14-18-25_11zon-1692369085-300x285.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FPHOTO-2023-04-05-14-18-25_11zon-1692369085-500x474.jpg%20500w%2C%20h